            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>This eBook is for the use of anyone anywhere at no cost and with\nalmost no restrictions whatsoever.  You may copy it, give it away or\nre-use it under the terms of the Project Gutenberg License included\nwith this eBook or online at www.gutenberg.org</p></div>"
