        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK SHI-JING ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by Christine Zeng and Qi-Ming publishing house</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">國風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>周南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>1.  關睢\n關關雎鳩、在河之洲。\n窈宨淑女、君子好逑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>參差荇菜、左右流之。\n窈宨淑女、寤寐求之。\n求之不得、寤寐思服。\n悠哉悠哉、輾轉反側。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>參差荇菜、左右采之。\n窈宨淑女、琴瑟友之。\n參差荇菜、左右芼之。\n窈宨淑女、 鍾鼓樂之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">2.  葛覃\n葛之覃兮、施于中谷。\n維葉萋萋、黃鳥于飛。\n集于灌木、其鳴喈喈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>葛之覃兮、施于中谷。\n維葉莫莫、是刈是濩。\n為絺為綌、服之無斁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>言告師氏、言告言歸。\n薄污我私、薄澣我衣。\n害澣害否、歸寧父母 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">3.   卷耳\n采采卷耳、不盈頃筐。\n嗟我懷人、寘彼周行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼崔嵬、我馬虺隤。\n我姑酌彼金罍、維以不永懷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼高岡、我馬玄黃。\n我姑酌彼兕觥、維以不永傷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼砠矣、我馬瘏矣、我僕痡矣、云何吁矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">4.  樛木\n南有樛木、葛藟纍之。\n樂只君子、福履綏之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南有樛木、葛藟荒之。\n樂只君子、福履將之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南有樛木、葛藟縈之。\n樂只君子、福履成之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">5.   螽斯\n螽斯羽、詵詵兮。\n宜爾子孫、振振兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>螽斯羽、薨薨兮。\n宜爾子孫、繩繩兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>螽斯羽、揖揖兮。\n宜爾子孫、蟄蟄兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">6.   桃夭\n桃之夭夭、灼灼其華。\n之子于歸、宜其家室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>桃之夭夭、有蕡其實。\n之子于歸、宜其室家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>桃之夭夭、其葉蓁蓁。\n之子于歸、宜其家人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">7.  兔罝\n肅肅兔罝、椓之丁丁。\n赳赳武夫、公侯干城。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肅肅兔罝、施于中逵。\n赳赳武夫、公侯好仇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肅肅兔罝、施于中林。\n赳赳武夫、公侯腹心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">8.  芣苡\n采采芣苡、薄言采之。\n采采芣苡、薄言有之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>采采芣苡、薄言掇之。\n采采芣苡、薄言捋之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>采采芣苡、薄言袺之。\n采采芣苡、薄言襭之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">9.  漢廣\n南有喬木、不可休息。\n漢有游女、不可求思。\n漢之廣矣、不可泳思。\n江之永矣、不可方思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>翹翹錯薪、言刈其楚。\n之子于歸、言秣其馬。\n漢之廣矣、不可泳思。\n江之永矣、不可方思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>翹翹錯薪、言刈其蔞 。\n之子于歸、言秣其駒 。\n漢之廣矣、不可泳思 。\n江之永矣、不可方思 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">10.  汝墳\n遵彼汝墳、伐其條枚。\n未見君子、惄如調飢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>遵彼汝墳、伐其條肆。\n既見君子、不我遐棄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>魴魚赬尾、王室如燬 。\n雖則如燬、父母孔邇 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">11.  麟之趾\n麟之趾、振振公子。\n于嗟麟兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>麟之定、振振公姓。\n于嗟麟兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>麟之角、振振公族。\n于嗟麟兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">召南</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>12.  鵲巢\n維鵲有巢、維鳩居之。\n之子于歸、百兩御之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維鵲有巢、維鳩方之。\n之子于歸、百兩將之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維鵲有巢、維鳩盈之。\n之子于歸、百兩成之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">13.  采蘩\n于以采蘩、于沼于沚。\n于以用之、公侯之事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>于以采蘩、于澗之中。\n于以用之、公侯之宮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>被之僮僮、夙夜在公。\n被之祁祁、薄言還歸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">14.  草蟲\n喓喓草蟲、趯趯阜螽\n未見君子、憂心忡忡。\n亦既見止、亦既覯止、我心則降。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼南山、言采其蕨。\n未見君子、憂心惙惙。\n亦既見止、亦既覯止、我心則說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼南山、言采其薇。\n未見君子、我心傷悲。\n亦既見止、亦既覯止、我心則夷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">15.  采蘋\n于以采蘋、南澗之濱。\n于以采藻、于彼行潦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>于以盛之、維筐及筥。\n于以湘之、維錡及釜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>于以奠之、宗室牖下。\n誰起尸之、有齊季女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">16.  甘棠\n蔽芾甘棠、勿翦勿伐、召伯所茇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蔽芾甘棠、勿翦勿敗、召伯所憩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蔽芾甘棠、勿翦勿拜、召伯所說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">17.  行露\n厭浥行露、豈不夙夜、謂行多露。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誰謂雀無角、何以穿我屋。\n誰謂女無家、何以速我獄。\n雖速我獄、室家不足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誰謂鼠無牙、何以穿我墉。\n誰謂女無家、何以速我訟。\n雖速我獄、亦不女從。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">18.  羔羊\n羔羊之皮、素絲五紽。\n退食自公、委蛇委蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>羔羊之革、素絲五緎。\n委蛇委蛇、自公退食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>羔羊之縫、素絲五總。\n委蛇委蛇、退食自公。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">19.  殷其雷\n殷其雷、在南山之陽。\n何斯違斯、莫敢或遑。\n振振君子、歸哉歸哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>殷其雷、在南山之側。\n何斯違斯、莫敢遑息。\n振振君子、歸哉歸哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>殷其雷、在南山之下。\n何斯違斯、莫敢遑處。\n振振君子、歸哉歸哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">20.   摽有梅\n摽有梅、其實七兮。\n求我庶士、迨其吉兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>摽有梅、其實三兮。\n求我庶士、迨其今兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>摽有梅、頃筐塈之。\n求我庶士、迨其謂之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">21.  小星\n嘒彼小星、三五在東。\n肅肅宵征、夙夜在公、寔命不同。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>嘒彼小星、 維參與昴。\n肅肅宵征、抱衾與裯、寔命不猶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">22.  江有汜\n江有汜、之子歸、不我以。\n不我以、其後也悔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>江有渚、之子歸、不我與。\n不我與、其後也處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>江有沱、之子歸、不我過。\n不我過、其嘯也歌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">23.  野有死麇\n野有死麇、白茅包之。\n有女懷春、吉士誘之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>林有樸樕、野有死鹿。\n白茅純束、有女如玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>舒而脫脫兮、無感我帨兮、無使尨也吠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">24.  何彼襛矣\n何彼襛矣、唐棣之華。\n曷不肅雝、王姬之車。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>何彼襛矣、華如桃李。\n平王之孫、齊侯之子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其釣維何、維絲伊緡。\n齊侯之子、平王之孫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">25.  騶虞\n彼茁者葭、壹發五豝。\n于嗟乎騶虞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼茁者蓬、壹發五豵。\n于嗟乎騶虞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">邶風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>26.  柏舟\n汎彼柏舟、亦汎其流。\n耿耿不寐、如有隱憂。\n微我無酒、以敖以遊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我心匪鑒、不可以茹。\n亦有兄弟、不可以據。\n薄言往愬、逢彼之怒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我心匪石、不可轉也。\n我心匪席、不可卷也。\n威儀棣棣、不可選也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>憂心悄悄、慍于群小。\n覯閔既多、受侮不少。\n靜言思之、寤辟有摽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>日居月諸、胡迭而微。\n心之憂矣、如匪澣衣。\n靜言思之、不能奮飛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">27.  綠衣\n綠兮衣兮、綠兮黃裏。\n心之憂矣、曷維其已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綠兮衣兮、綠兮黃裳。\n心之憂矣、曷維其亡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綠兮絲兮、女所治兮。\n我思古人、俾無訧兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>稀兮綌兮、淒其以風。\n我思古人、實獲我心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">28.  燕燕\n燕燕于飛、差池其羽。\n之子于歸、遠送于野。\n瞻望弗及、泣涕如雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>燕燕于飛、頡之頏之。\n之子于歸、遠于將之。\n瞻望弗及、佇立以泣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>燕燕于飛、下上其音。\n之子于歸、遠送于南。\n瞻望弗及、實勞我心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>仲氏任只、其心塞淵。\n終溫且惠、淑慎其身。\n先君之思、以勗寡人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">29.  日月\n日居月諸、照臨下土。\n乃如之人兮、逝不古處。\n胡能有定、寧不我顧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>日居月諸、下土是冒。\n乃如之人兮、逝不相好。\n胡能有定、寧不我報。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>日居月諸、出自東方。\n乃如之人兮、德音無良。\n胡能有定、俾也可忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>日居月諸、東方自出。\n父兮母兮、畜我不卒。\n胡能有定、報我不述。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">30.  終風\n終風且暴、顧我則笑。\n謔浪笑敖、中心是悼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>終風且霾、惠然肯來。\n莫往莫來、悠悠我思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>終風且曀、不日有曀。\n寤言不寐、願言則嚏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>曀曀其陰、虺虺其雷。\n寤言不寐、願言則懷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">31.  擊鼓\n擊鼓其鏜、踊躍用兵。\n土國城漕、我獨南行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>從孫子仲、平陳與宋。\n不我以歸、憂心有忡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爰居爰處、爰喪其馬。\n于以求之、于林之下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>死生契闊、與子成說。\n執子之手、與子偕老。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>于嗟闊兮、不我活兮。\n于嗟洵兮、不我信兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">32.  凱風\n凱風自南、吹彼棘心。\n棘心夭夭、母氏劬勞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>凱風自南、吹彼棘薪。\n母氏聖善、我無令人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爰有寒泉、在浚之下。\n有子七人、母氏勞苦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>睍睆黃鳥、載好其音。\n有子其人、莫慰母心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">33.  雄雉\n雄雉于飛、泄泄其羽。\n我之懷矣、自詒伊阻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>雄雉于飛、下上其音。\n展矣君子、實勞我心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼日月、悠悠我思。\n道之云遠、曷云能來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>百爾君子、不知德行。\n不忮不求、何用不臧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">34.  匏有苦葉\n匏有苦葉、濟有深涉。\n深則厲、淺則揭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有瀰濟盈、有鷕雉鳴。\n濟盈不濡軌、雉鳴求起牡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>雝雝鳴鴈、旭日始旦。\n士如歸妻、迨冰未泮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>招招舟子、人涉卬否。\n人涉卬否、卬須我友。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">35.  谷風\n習習谷風、以陰以雨。\n黽勉同心、不宜有怒。\n采封采菲、無以下體。\n德音莫違、及爾同死。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>行道遲遲、中心有違。\n不遠伊邇、薄送我畿。\n誰謂荼苦、其甘如薺。\n宴爾新昏、如兄如弟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>涇以渭濁、湜湜其沚。\n宴爾新昏、不我屑以。\n毋逝我梁、毋發我笱。\n我躬不閱、遑恤我後。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>就其深矣、方之舟之。\n就其淺矣、泳之游之。\n何有何亡、黽勉求之。\n凡民有喪、匍匐救之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>不我能慉、反以我為讎。\n既阻我德、賈用不售。\n昔育恐育鞫、及爾顛覆。\n既生既育、比予于毒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我有旨蓄、亦以御冬。\n宴爾新昏、以我御窮。\n有洸有潰、既詒我肄。\n不念昔者、伊余來塈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">36.  式微\n式微式微、胡不歸。\n微君之故、胡為乎中露。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>式微式微、胡不歸。\n微君之躬、胡為乎泥中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">37.  旄丘\n旄丘之葛兮、何誕之節兮。\n叔兮伯兮、何多日也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>何其處也、必有與也。\n何其久也、必有以也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>狐裘蒙戎、匪車不東。\n叔兮伯兮、靡所與同。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瑣兮尾兮、流離之子。\n叔兮伯兮、褎如充耳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">38.  簡兮\n簡兮簡兮、方將萬舞。\n日之方中、在前上處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>碩人俁俁、公庭萬舞。\n有力如虎、執轡如組。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>左手執籥、右手秉翟。\n赫如渥赭、公言錫爵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有榛、隰有苓。\n云誰之思、西方美人。\n彼美人兮、西方之人兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">39.  泉水\n毖彼泉水、亦流于淇。\n有懷于衛、靡日不思。\n孌彼諸姬、聊與之謀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>出宿于泲、飲餞于禰。\n女子有行、遠父母兄弟。\n問我諸姑、遂及伯姊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>出宿于干、飲餞于言。\n載脂載牽、還車言邁。\n遄臻于衛、不瑕有害。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我思肥泉、茲之永歎。\n思須與漕、我心悠悠。\n駕言出游、以寫我憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">40.  北門\n出自北門、憂心殷殷。\n終窶且貧、莫知我艱。\n已焉哉、天實為之、謂之何哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王事適我、政事一埤益我。\n我入自外、室人交遍謫我。\n已焉哉、天實為之、謂之何哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王事敦我、政事一埤遺我。\n我入自外、室人交遍摧我。\n已焉哉、天實為之、謂之何哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">41.  北風\n北風其涼、雨雪其雱。\n惠而好我、攜手同行。\n其虛其邪、既亟只且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>北風其喈、雨雪其霏。\n惠而好我、攜手同歸。\n其虛其邪、既亟只且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>莫赤匪狐、莫黑匪烏。\n惠而好我、攜手同車。\n其虛其邪、既亟只且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">42.  靜女\n靜女其姝、俟我於城隅。\n愛而不見、搔首踟躕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>靜女其孌、貽我彤管。\n彤管有煒、說懌女美。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>自牧歸荑、洵美且異。\n匪女以為美、美人之貽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">43.  新臺\n新臺有沘、河水彌彌。\n燕婉之求、籧篨不鮮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>新臺有洒、河水浼浼。\n燕婉之求、籧篨不殄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>魚網之設、鴻則離之。\n燕婉之求、得此戚施。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">44.  二子乘舟\n二子乘舟、汎汎其景。\n願言思子、中心養養。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>二子乘舟、汎汎其逝。\n願言思子、不瑕有害。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">鄘風\n45.  柏舟\n汎彼柏舟、在彼中河。\n髧彼兩髦、實維我儀。\n之死矢靡它。\n母也天只、不諒人只。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>汎彼柏舟、在彼河側。\n髧彼兩髦、實維我特。\n之死矢靡慝。\n母也天只、不諒人只。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">46.  牆有茨\n牆有茨、不可埽也。\n中冓之言、不可道也。\n所可道也、言之醜也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>牆有茨、不可襄也。\n中冓之言、不可詳也。\n所可詳也、言之長也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>牆有茨、不可束也。\n中冓之言、不可讀也。\n所可讀也、言之辱也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">47.  君子偕老\n君子偕老、副笄六珈。\n委委佗佗、如山如河、象服是宜。\n子之不淑、云如之何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>玼兮玼兮、其之翟也。\n鬒髮如云、不屑也。\n玉之瑱也、象之揥也、揚且之皙也。\n胡然而天也、胡然而帝也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瑳兮瑳兮、其之展也。\n蒙彼縐絺、是紲袢也。\n子之清揚、揚且之顏也。\n展如之人兮、邦之媛也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">48.  桑中\n爰采唐矣、沬之鄉矣。\n云誰之思、美孟姜矣。\n期我乎桑中、要我乎上宮、送我乎淇之上矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爰采麥矣、沬之北矣。\n云誰之思、美孟弋矣。\n期我乎桑中、要我乎上宮、送我乎淇之上矣 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爰采葑矣、沬之東矣。\n云誰之思、美孟庸矣。\n期我乎桑中、要我乎上宮、送我乎淇之上矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">49.  鶉之奔奔\n鶉之奔奔、鵲之彊彊。\n人之無良、我以為兄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鵲之彊彊、鶉之奔奔。\n人之無良、我以為君。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">50.  定之方中\n定之方中、作于楚宮。\n揆之以日、作于楚室。\n樹之榛栗、椅桐梓漆、爰伐琴瑟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>升彼虛矣、以望楚矣。\n望楚與堂、景山與京。\n降觀于桑、卜云其吉、終然允臧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>靈雨既零、命彼倌人。\n星言夙駕、說于桑田。\n匪直也人、秉心塞淵、騋牝三千。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">51.  蝃蝀\n蝃蝀在東、莫之敢指。\n女子有行、遠兄弟父母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>朝隮于西、崇朝其雨。\n女子有行、遠兄弟父母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乃如之人也、懷昏姻也。\n大無信也、不知命也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">52.  相鼠\n相鼠有皮、人而無儀。\n人而無儀、不死何為。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>相鼠有齒、人而無止。\n人而無止、不死何俟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>相鼠有體、人而無禮。\n人而無禮、胡不遄死。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">53.  干旄\n孑孑干旄、在浚之郊。\n素絲紕之、良馬四之。\n彼姝者之、何以畀之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>孑孑干旟、在浚之都。\n素絲組之、良馬五之。\n彼姝者之、何以予之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>孑孑干旌、在浚之城。\n素絲祝之、良馬六之。\n彼姝者之、何以告之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">54.  載馳\n載馳載驅、歸唁衛侯。\n驅馬悠悠、言至于漕。\n大夫跋涉、我心則憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>既不我嘉、不能旋反。\n視而不臧、我思不遠。\n既不我嘉、不能旋濟。\n視而不臧、我思不閟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼阿丘、言采其虻。\n女子善懷、亦各有行。\n許人尤之、眾樨且狂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我行其野、芃芃其麥。\n控于大邦、誰因誰極。\n大夫君子、無我有尤。\n百爾所思、不如我所之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">衛風\n55.  淇奧\n瞻彼淇奧、綠竹猗猗。\n有匪君子、如切如磋、如琢如磨。\n瑟兮僩兮、赫兮咺兮。\n有匪君子、終不可諼兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼淇奧、綠竹青青。\n有匪君子、充耳琇瑩、會弁如星。\n瑟兮僩兮、赫兮咺兮。\n有匪君子、終不可諼兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼淇奧、綠竹如簀。\n有匪君子、如切如錫、如圭如璧。\n寬兮綽兮、猗重較兮。\n善戲謔兮、不為虐兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">56.  考槃\n考槃在澗、碩人之寬。\n獨寐寤言、永矢弗諼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>考槃在阿、碩人之薖。\n獨寐寤歌、永矢弗過。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>考槃在陸、碩人之軸。\n獨寐寤宿、永矢弗告。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">57.  碩人\n碩人其頎、衣錦褧衣。\n齊侯之子、衛侯之妻、東宮之妹、邢侯之姨、譚公維私。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>手如柔荑。\n膚如凝脂。\n領如蝤蠐。\n領如蝤蠐。\n齒如瓠犀。\n螓首蛾眉。\n巧笑倩兮。\n美目盼兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>碩人敖敖、說于農郊。\n四牡有驕、朱幩鑣鑣、翟茀以朝。\n大夫夙退、無使君勞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>河水洋洋、北流活活。\n施罛瀖瀖、鱣鮪發發、葭菼揭揭。\n庶姜孽孽、庶士有朅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">58.  氓\n氓之蚩蚩、抱布貿絲。\n匪來貿絲、來即我謀。\n送子涉淇、至于頓丘。\n匪來愆期、子無良媒。\n將子無怒、秋以為期。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乘彼垝垣、以望復關。\n不見復關、泣涕漣漣。\n既見復關、載笑載言。\n爾卜爾筮、體無咎言。\n以爾車來、以我賄遷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>桑之未落、其葉沃若。\n于嗟鳩兮、無食桑葚。\n于嗟女兮、無與士耽。\n士之耽兮、猶可說也、\n女之耽兮、 不可說也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>桑之落矣、其黃而隕。\n自我徂爾、三歲食貧。\n淇水湯湯、漸車帷裳。\n女也不爽、士貳其行。\n士也罔極、二三其德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>三歲為婦、靡室勞矣。\n夙興夜寐、靡有朝矣。\n言既遂矣、至于暴矣。\n兄弟不知、咥其笑矣。\n靜言思之、躬自悼矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>及爾偕老、老使我怨。\n淇則有岸、隰則有泮。\n總角之宴、言笑晏晏。\n信膂旦旦、不思其反。\n反是不思、亦已焉哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">59.  竹竿\n藋藋竹竿、以釣于淇。\n豈不爾思、遠莫致之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>泉源在左、淇水在右。\n女子有行、遠兄弟父母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>淇水在右、泉源在左。\n巧笑之瑎、佩玉之儺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>淇水浟浟、檜楫松舟。\n駕言出遊、以寫我憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">60.  芄蘭\n芄蘭之支、童子佩觿。\n雖則佩觿、能不我知。\n容兮遂兮、垂帶悸兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>芄蘭之葉、童子佩韘。\n雖則佩韘、能不我甲。\n容兮遂兮、垂帶悸兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">61.  河廣\n誰謂河廣、一葦杭之。\n誰謂宋遠、跂予望之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誰謂河廣、曾不容刀。\n誰謂宋遠、曾不崇朝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">62.  伯兮\n伯兮朅兮、邦之桀兮。\n伯也執殳、為王前驅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>自伯之東、首如飛蓬。\n豈無膏沐、誰適為容。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其雨其雨、杲杲出日。\n願言思伯、甘心首疾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>焉得諼草、言樹之背。\n願言思伯、使我心痗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">63.  有狐\n有狐綏綏、在彼淇梁。\n心之憂矣、之子無裳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有狐綏綏、在彼淇厲。\n心之憂矣、之子無帶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有狐綏綏、在彼淇側。\n心之憂矣、之子無服。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">64.  木瓜\n投我以木瓜、報之以瓊琚。\n匪報也、永以為好也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>投我以木桃、報之以瓊瑤。\n匪報也、永以為好也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>投我以木李、報之以瓊玖。\n匪報也、永以為好也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">王風\n65.  黍離\n彼黍離離、彼稷之苗。\n行邁靡靡、中心搖搖。\n知我者、謂我心憂、不知我者、謂我何求。\n悠悠蒼天、此何人哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼黍離離、彼稷之穗。\n行邁靡靡、中心如醉。\n知我者、謂我心憂、不知我者、謂我何求。\n悠悠蒼天、此何人哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼黍離離、彼稷之實。\n行邁靡靡、中心如噎。\n知我者、謂我心憂、不知我者、謂我何求。\n悠悠蒼天、此何人哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">66.  君子于役\n君子于役、不知其期、曷至哉。\n雞棲于塒、日之夕矣、羊牛下來。\n君子于役、如之何勿思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>君子于役、不日不月、曷其有佸。\n雞棲于桀、日之夕矣、羊牛下括。\n君子于役、茍無飢渴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">67.  君子陽陽\n君子陽陽、左執簧、右招我由房。\n其樂只且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>君子陶陶、左執翿、右招我由敖。\n其樂只且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">68.  揚之水\n揚之水、不流束薪。\n彼其之子、不與我戍申。\n懷哉懷哉、曷月予還歸哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>揚之水、不流束楚。\n彼其之子、不與我戍甫。\n懷哉懷哉、曷月予還歸哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>揚之水、不流束蒲。\n彼其之子、不與我戍許。\n懷哉懷哉、曷月予還歸哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">69.  中谷有蓷\n中谷有蓷、暵其乾矣。\n有女仳離、慨其歎矣。\n慨其歎矣、遇人之艱難矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>中谷有蓷、暵其修矣。\n有女仳離、條其嘯矣。\n慨其嘯矣、遇人之不淑矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>中谷有蓷、暵其濕矣。\n有女仳離、啜其泣矣。\n啜其泣矣、嗟何及矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">70.  兔爰\n有兔爰爰、雉離于羅。\n我生之初、尚無為。\n我生之後、逢此百罹。\n尚寐無吪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有兔爰爰、雉離于罦。\n我生之初、尚無造。\n我生之後、逢此百憂。\n尚寐無覺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有兔爰爰、雉離于罿。\n我生之初、尚無庸。\n我生之後、逢此百凶。\n尚寐無聰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">71.  葛藟\n綿綿葛藟、在河之滸。\n終遠兄弟、謂他人父。\n謂他人父、亦莫我顧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綿綿葛藟、在河之涘。\n終遠兄弟、謂他人母。\n謂他人母、亦莫我有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綿綿葛藟、在河之漘。\n終遠兄弟、謂他人昆。\n謂他人昆、亦莫我聞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">72.  采葛\n彼采葛兮。\n一日不見、如三月兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼采蕭兮。\n一日不見、如三秋兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼采艾兮。\n一日不見、如三歲兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">73.  大車\n大車檻檻、毳衣如菼。\n豈不爾思、畏子不敢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>大車啍啍、毳衣如璊。\n豈不爾思、畏子不奔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>穀則異室、死則同穴。\n謂予不信、有如皦日。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">74.  丘中有麻\n丘中有麻、彼留子嗟。\n彼留子嗟、將其來施施。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>丘中有麥、彼留子國。\n彼留子國、將其來食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>丘中有李、彼留之子。\n彼留之子、貽我佩玖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">鄭風\n75.  緇衣\n緇衣之宜兮、敝、予又改為兮。\n適子之館兮、還、予授子之粲兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>緇衣之好兮、敝、予又改造兮。\n適子之館兮、還、予授子之粲兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>緇衣之蓆兮、敝、予又改作兮。\n適子之館兮、還、予授子之粲兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">76.  將仲子\n將仲子兮、無踰我里、無折我樹杞。\n豈敢愛之、畏我父母。\n仲可懷也、父母之言、亦可畏也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>將仲子兮、無踰我墻、無折我樹桑。\n豈敢愛之、畏我諸兄。\n仲可懷也、諸兄之言、亦可畏也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>將仲子兮、無踰我園、無折我樹檀。\n豈敢愛之、畏人之多言。\n仲可懷也、人之多言、亦可畏也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">77.  叔于田\n叔于田、巷無居人。\n豈無居人、不如叔也、洵美且仁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>叔于狩、巷無飲酒。\n豈無飲酒、不如叔也、洵美且好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>叔適野、巷無服馬。\n豈無服馬、不如叔也、洵美且武。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">78.  大叔于田\n叔于田、乘乘馬、執轡如組、兩驂如舞。\n叔在藪、火烈具舉。\n襢裼暴虎、獻于公所。\n將叔無狃、戒其傷女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>叔于田、乘乘黃、兩服上襄、兩驂雁行。\n叔在藪、火烈具揚。\n叔善射忌、又良御忌、抑磬控忌、抑縱送忌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>叔于田、乘乘鴇、兩服齊首、兩驂如手。\n叔在藪、火烈具阜。\n叔馬慢忌、叔發罕忌、抑釋掤忌、抑鬯弓忌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">79.  清人\n清人在彭、駟介旁旁、二矛重英、河上乎翱翔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>清人在消、駟介麃麃、二矛重喬、河上乎逍遙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>清人在軸、駟介陶陶、左旋右抽、中軍作好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">80.  羔裘\n羔裘如濡、洵直且侯。\n彼其之子、舍命不渝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>羔裘豹飾、孔武有力。\n彼其之子、邦之司直。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>羔裘晏兮、三英粲兮。\n彼其之子、邦之彥兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">81.  遵大路\n遵大路兮、摻執子之怯兮。\n無我惡兮、不寁故也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>遵大路兮、摻執子之手兮。\n無我醜兮、不寁好也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">82.  女曰雞鳴\n女曰雞鳴、士曰昧旦。\n子興視夜、明星有爛。\n將翱將翔、弋鳧與雁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>弋言加之、與子宜之。\n宜言飲酒、與子偕老。\n琴瑟在御、莫不靜好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>知子之來之、雜佩以贈之。\n知子之順之、雜佩以問之。\n知子之好之、雜佩以報之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">83.  有女同車\n有女同車、顏如舜華。\n將翱將翔、佩玉瓊琚。\n彼美孟姜、洵美且都。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有女同行、顏如舜英。\n將翱將翔、佩玉將將。\n彼美孟姜、德音不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">84.  山有扶蘇\n山有扶蘇、隰有荷華。\n不見子都、乃見狂且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有橋松、隰有游龍。\n不見子充、乃見狡童。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">85.  蘀兮\n蘀兮蘀兮、風其吹女。\n叔兮伯兮、倡予和女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蘀兮蘀兮、風其漂女。\n叔兮伯兮、倡予要女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">86.  狡童\n彼狡童兮、不與我言兮。\n維子之故、使我不能餐兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼狡童兮、不與我食兮。\n維子之故、使我不能息兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">87.  褰裳\n子惠思我、褰裳涉溱。\n子不我思、豈無他人。\n狂童之狂也且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>子惠思我、褰裳涉洧。\n子不我思、豈無他士。\n狂童之狂也且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">88.  丰\n子之丰兮、俟我乎巷兮。\n悔予不送兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>子之昌兮、俟我乎堂兮。\n悔予不將兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>衣錦褧裳、裳錦褧裳。\n叔兮伯兮、駕予與行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>裳錦褧裳、衣錦褧衣。\n叔兮伯兮、駕予與歸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">89.  東門之墠\n東門之墠、茹藘在阪。\n其室則邇、其人甚遠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東門之栗、有踐家室。\n豈不爾思、子不我即。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">90.  風雨\n風雨淒淒、雞鳴喈喈。\n既見君子、云胡不夷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>風雨瀟瀟、雞鳴膠膠。\n既見君子、云胡不瘳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>風雨如晦、雞鳴不已。\n既見君子、云胡不喜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">91.  子衿\n青青子衿、悠悠我心。\n縱我不往、子寧不嗣音。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>青青子佩、悠悠我思。\n縱我不往、子寧不來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>挑兮達兮、在城闕兮。\n一日不見、如三月兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">92.  揚之水\n揚之水、不流束楚。\n終鮮兄弟、維予與女。\n無信人之言、人實迋女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>揚之水、不流束薪。\n終鮮兄弟、維予二人。\n無信人之言、人實不信。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">93.  出其東門\n出其東門、有女如雲。\n雖則如雲、匪我思存。\n縞衣綦巾、聊樂我員。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>出其闉闍、有女如荼。\n雖則如荼、匪我思且。\n縞衣茹藘、聊可與娛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">94.  野有蔓草\n野有蔓草、零露漙兮。\n有美一人、清揚婉兮。\n邂逅相遇、適我願兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>野有蔓草、零露瀼瀼。\n有美一人、婉如清揚。\n邂逅相遇、與子偕臧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">95.  溱洧\n溱與洧、方渙渙兮。\n士與女、方秉蘭兮。\n女曰觀乎。\n士曰既且。\n且往觀乎。\n洧之外、洵訏且樂。\n維士與女、伊其相謔、贈之以勺藥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>溱與洧、瀏其清矣。\n士與女、殷其盈兮。\n女曰觀乎。\n士曰既且。\n且往觀乎。\n洧之外、洵訏且樂。\n維士與女、伊其將謔、贈之以勺藥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">齊風\n96.  雞鳴\n雞既鳴矣、朝既盈矣。\n匪雞則鳴、蒼蠅之聲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東方明矣、朝既昌矣。\n匪東方則明、月出之光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蟲飛薨薨、甘與子同夢。\n會且歸矣、無庶予子憎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">97.  還\n子之還兮、遭我乎峱之間兮。\n並驅從兩肩兮、揖我謂我儇兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>子之茂兮、遭我乎峱之道兮。\n並驅從兩牡兮、揖我謂我好兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>子之昌兮、遭我乎峱之陽兮。\n並驅從兩狼兮、揖我謂我臧兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">98.  著\n俟我於著乎而、充耳以素乎而、尚之以瓊華乎而。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>俟我於庭乎而、充耳以青乎而、尚之以瓊瑩乎而。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>俟我於堂乎而、充耳以黃乎而、尚之以瓊英乎而。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">99.  東方之日\n東方之日兮。\n彼姝者子、在我室兮。\n在我室兮、履我即兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東方之月兮。\n彼姝者子、在我闥兮。\n在我闥兮、履我發兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">100.  東方未明\n東方未明、顛倒衣裳。\n顛之倒之、自公召之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東方未晞、顛倒裳衣。\n倒之顛之、自公令之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>折柳樊圃、狂夫瞿瞿。\n不能辰夜、不夙則莫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">101.  南山\n南山崔崔、雄狐綏綏。\n魯道有蕩、齊子由歸。\n既曰歸止、曷又懷止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>葛屨五兩、冠緌雙止。\n魯道有蕩、齊子庸止。\n既曰庸止、曷又從止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蓺麻如之何、衡從其畝。\n取妻如之何、必告父母。\n既曰告止、曷又鞠止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>析薪如之何、匪斧不克。\n取妻如之何、匪媒不得。\n既曰得止、曷又極止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">102.  甫田\n無田甫田、維莠驕驕。\n無思遠人、勞心忉忉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>無田甫田、維莠桀桀。\n無思遠人、勞心怛怛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>婉兮孌兮、總角丱兮。\n未幾見兮、突而弁兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">103.  盧令\n盧令令、其人美且仁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>盧重環、其人美且鬈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>盧重鋂、其人美且偲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">104.  敝笱\n敝笱在梁、其魚魴鰥。\n齊子歸止、其從如雲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>敝笱在梁、其魚魴鱮。\n齊子歸止、其從如雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>敝笱在梁、其魚唯唯。\n齊子歸止、其從如水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">105.  載驅\n載驅薄薄、簟茀朱鞹。\n魯道有蕩、齊子發夕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四驪濟濟、垂轡濔濔。\n魯道有蕩、齊子豈弟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>汶水湯湯、行人彭彭。\n魯道有蕩、齊子翱翔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>汶水滔滔、行人儦儦。\n魯道有蕩、齊子游遨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">106.  猗嗟\n猗嗟昌兮、頎而長兮、抑若揚兮、美目揚兮。\n巧趨蹌兮、射則臧兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>猗嗟名兮、美目清兮。\n儀既成兮。\n終日射侯、不出正兮。\n展我甥兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>猗嗟孌兮、清揚婉兮。\n舞則選兮、射則貫兮。\n四矢反兮、以禦亂兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">魏風\n107.  葛屨\n糾糾葛屨、可以履霜。\n摻摻女手、可以縫裳。\n要之襋之、好人服之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>好人提提、宛然左辟、佩其象揥。\n維是褊心、是以為刺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">108.  汾沮洳\n彼汾沮洳、言采其莫。\n彼其之子、美無度。\n美無度、殊異乎公路。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼汾一方、言采其桑。\n彼其之子、美如英。\n美如英、殊異乎公行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼汾一曲、言采其藚。\n彼其之子、美如玉。\n美如玉、殊異乎公族。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">109.  園有桃\n園有桃、其實之殽。\n心之憂矣、我歌且謠。\n不我知者、謂我士也驕。\n彼人是哉、子曰何其。\n心之憂矣、其誰知之。\n其誰知之、蓋亦勿思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>園有棘、其實之食。\n心之憂矣、聊以行國。\n不我知者、謂我士也罔極。\n彼人是哉、子曰何其。\n心之憂矣、其誰知之。\n其誰知之、蓋亦勿思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">110.  陟岵\n陟彼岵兮、瞻望父兮。\n父曰嗟、予子行役、夙夜無已。\n上慎旃哉、猶來無止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼屺兮、瞻望母兮。\n母曰嗟、予季行役、夙夜無寐。\n上慎旃哉、猶來無棄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼岡兮、瞻望兄兮。\n兄曰嗟、予弟行役、夙夜必偕。\n上慎旃哉、猶來無死。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">111.  十畝之間\n十畝之閒兮、桑者閑閑兮。\n行與子還兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>十畝之外兮、桑者泄泄兮。\n行與子逝兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">112.  伐檀\n坎坎伐檀兮、寘之河之干兮、河水清且漣猗。\n不稼不穡、胡取禾三百廛兮。\n不狩不獵、胡瞻爾庭有縣貆兮。\n彼君子兮、不素餐兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>坎坎伐輻兮、寘之河之側兮、河水清且直猗。\n不稼不穡、胡取禾三百億兮。\n不狩不獵、胡瞻爾庭有縣特兮。\n彼君子兮、不素食兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>坎坎伐輪兮、寘之河之漘兮、河水清且淪猗。\n不稼不穡、胡取禾三百囷兮。\n不狩不獵、胡瞻爾庭有縣鶉兮。\n彼君子兮、不素飧兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">113.  碩鼠\n碩鼠碩鼠、無食我黍。\n三歲貫女、莫我肯顧。\n逝將去女、適彼樂土。\n樂土樂土、爰得我所。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>碩鼠碩鼠、無食我麥。\n三歲貫女、莫我肯德。\n逝將去女、適彼樂國。\n樂國樂國、爰得我直。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>碩鼠碩鼠、無食我苗。\n三歲貫女、莫我肯勞。\n逝將去女、適彼樂郊。\n樂郊樂郊、誰之永號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">唐風\n114.  蟋蟀\n蟋蟀在堂、歲聿其莫。\n今我不樂、日月其除。\n無已大康、職思其居。\n好樂無荒、良士瞿瞿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蟋蟀在堂、歲聿其逝。\n今我不樂、日月其邁。\n無已大康、職思其外。\n好樂無荒、良士蹶蹶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蟋蟀在堂、役車其休。\n今我不樂、日月其慆。\n無已大康、職思其憂。\n好樂無荒、良士休休。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">115.  山有樞\n山有樞、隰有榆。\n子有衣裳、弗曳弗婁。\n子有車馬、弗馳弗驅。\n宛其死矣、他人是愉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有栲、隰有杻。\n子有廷內、弗洒弗埽。\n子有鐘鼓、弗鼓弗考。\n宛其死矣、他人是保。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有漆、隰有栗。\n子有酒食、何不日鼓瑟。\n且以喜樂、且以永日。\n宛其死矣、他人入室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">116.  揚之水\n揚之水、白石鑿鑿。\n素衣朱襮、從子于沃。\n既見君子、云何不樂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>揚之水、白石皓皓。\n素衣朱繡、從子于鵠。\n既見君子、云何其憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>揚之水、白石粼粼。\n我聞有命、不敢以告人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">117.  椒聊\n椒聊之實、蕃衍盈升。\n彼其之子、碩大無朋。\n椒聊且、遠條且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>椒聊之實、蕃衍盈匊。\n彼其之子、碩大且篤。\n椒聊且、遠條且。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">118.  綢繆\n綢繆束薪、三星在天。\n今夕何夕、見此良人。\n子兮子兮、如此良人何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綢繆束芻、三星在隅。\n今夕何夕、見此邂逅。\n子兮子兮、如此邂逅何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綢繆束楚、三星在戶。\n今夕何夕、見此粲者。\n子兮子兮、如此粲者何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">119.  杕杜\n有杕之杜、其葉湑湑。\n獨行踽踽。\n豈無他人、不如我同父。\n嗟行之人、胡不比焉。\n人無兄弟、胡不佽焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有杕之杜、其葉菁菁。\n獨行瞏瞏。\n豈無他人、不如我同姓。\n嗟行之人、胡不比焉。\n人無兄弟、胡不佽焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">120.  羔裘\n羔裘豹祛、自我人居居。\n豈無他人、維子之故。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>羔裘豹褎、自我人究究。\n豈無他人、維子之好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">121.  鴇羽\n肅肅鴇羽、集于苞栩。\n王事靡盬、不能蓺稷黍、父母何怙。\n悠悠蒼天、曷其有所。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肅肅鴇翼、集于苞棘。\n王事靡盬、不能蓺黍稷、父母何食。\n悠悠蒼天、曷其有極。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肅肅鴇行、集于苞桑。\n王事靡盬、不能蓺稻粱、父母何嘗。\n悠悠蒼天、曷其有常。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">122.  無衣\n豈曰無衣七兮、不如子之衣、安且吉兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>豈曰無衣六兮、不如子之衣、安且燠兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">123.  有杕之杜\n有杕之杜、生于道左。\n彼君子兮、噬肯適我。\n中心好之、曷飲食之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有杕之杜、生于道周。\n彼君子兮、噬肯來游。\n中心好之、曷飲食之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">124.  葛生\n葛生蒙楚、蘞蔓于野。\n予美亡此、誰與獨處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>葛生蒙棘、蘞蔓于域。\n予美亡此、誰與獨息。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>角枕粲兮、錦衾爛兮。\n予美亡此、誰與獨旦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>夏之日、冬之夜、百歲之後、歸於其居。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>冬之夜、夏之日、百歲之後、歸於其室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">125.  采苓\n采苓采苓、首陽之巔。\n人之為言、苟亦無信。\n舍旃舍旃、苟亦無然。\n人之為言、胡得焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>采苦采苦、首陽之下。\n人之為言、苟亦無與。\n舍旃舍旃、苟亦無然。\n人之為言、胡得焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>采葑采葑、首陽之東。\n人之無言、苟亦無從。\n舍旃舍旃、苟亦無然。\n人之為言、胡得焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">秦風\n126.  車鄰\n有車鄰鄰、有馬白顛。\n未見君子、寺人之令。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>阪有漆、隰有栗。\n既見君子、並坐鼓瑟。\n今者不樂、逝者其耋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>阪有桑、隰有楊。\n既見君子、並坐鼓簧。\n今者不樂、逝者其亡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">127.  駟驖\n駟驖孔阜、六轡在手。\n公之媚子、從公于狩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>奉時辰牡、辰牡孔碩。\n公曰左之、舍拔則獲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>遊于北園、四馬既閑。\n輶車鸞鑣、載獫歇驕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">128.  小戎\n小戎俴收、五楘梁輈。\n游環脅驅、陰靷鋈續、文茵暢轂、駕我騏馵。\n言念君子、溫其如玉。\n在其板屋、亂我心曲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四牡孔阜、六轡在手、騏騮是中、騧驪是驂、龍盾之合、鋈以觼軜。\n言念君子、溫其在邑。\n方何為期、胡然我念之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>俴駟孔群、厹矛鋈錞、蒙伐有苑、虎韔鏤膺、交韔二弓、竹閉緄滕。\n言念君子、載寢載與。\n厭厭良人、秩秩德音。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">129.  蒹葭\n蒹葭蒼蒼、白露為霜。\n所謂伊人、在水一方。\n溯洄從之、道阻且長。\n溯游從之、宛在水中央。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蒹葭淒淒、白露未晞。\n所謂伊人、在水之湄。\n溯洄從之、道阻且躋。\n溯游從之、宛在水中坻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蒹葭采采、白露未已。\n所謂伊人、在水之涘。\n溯洄從之、道阻且右。\n溯游從之、宛在水中沚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">130.  終南\n終南何有、有條有梅。\n君子至止、錦衣狐裘。\n顏如渥丹、其君也哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>終南何有、有紀有堂。\n君子至止、黻衣繡裳、佩玉將將、壽考不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">131.  黃鳥\n交交黃鳥、止于棘。\n誰從穆公、子車奄息。\n維此奄息、百夫之特。\n臨其穴、惴惴其慄。\n彼蒼者天、殲我良人。\n如可贖兮、人百其身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>交交黃鳥、止于桑。\n誰從穆公、子車仲行。\n維此仲行、百夫之防。\n臨其穴、惴惴其慄。\n彼蒼者天、殲我良人。\n如可贖兮、人百其身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>交交黃鳥、止于楚。\n誰從穆公、子車鍼虎。\n維此鍼虎、百夫之禦。\n臨其穴、惴惴其慄。\n彼蒼者天、殲我良人。\n如可贖兮、人百其身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">132.  晨風\n歍彼晨風、鬱彼北林。\n未見君子、憂心欽欽。\n如何如何、忘我實多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有苞櫟、隰有六駁。\n未見君子、憂心靡樂。\n如何如何、忘我實多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有苞棣、隰有樹檖。\n未見君子、憂心如醉。\n如何如何、忘我實多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">133.  無衣\n豈曰無衣、與子同袍。\n王于興師、修我戈矛、與子同仇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>豈曰無衣、與子同澤。\n王于興師、修我矛戟、與子偕作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>豈曰無衣、與子同裳。\n王于興師、修我甲兵、與子偕行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">134.  渭陽\n我送舅氏、曰至渭陽。\n何以贈之、路車乘黃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我送舅氏、悠悠我思。\n何以贈之、瓊瑰玉佩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">135.  權輿\n於我乎、夏屋渠渠、今也每食無餘。\n于嗟乎、不承權輿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>於我乎、每食四簋、今也每食不飽。\n于嗟乎、不承權輿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">陳風\n136.  宛丘\n子之湯兮、宛丘之上兮。\n洵有情兮、而無望兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>坎其擊鼓、宛丘之下。\n無冬無夏、值其鷺羽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>坎其擊缶、宛丘之道。\n無冬無夏、值其鷺翿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">137.  東門之枌\n東門之枌、宛丘之栩。\n子仲之子、婆娑其下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>穀旦于差、南方之原。\n不績其麻、市也婆娑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>穀旦于逝、越以鬷邁。\n視爾如荍、貽我握椒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">138.  衡門\n衡門之下、可以棲遲。\n泌之洋洋、可以樂飢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>豈其食魚、必河之魴。\n豈其取妻、必齊之姜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>豈其食魚、必河之鯉。\n豈其取妻、必宋之子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">139.  東門之池\n東門之池、可以漚麻。\n彼美淑姬、可與晤歌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東門之池、可以漚紵。\n彼美淑姬、可與晤語。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東門之池、可以漚菅。\n彼美淑姬、可與晤言。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">140.  東門之楊\n東門之楊、其葉牂牂。\n昏以為期、明星煌煌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東門之楊、其葉肺肺。\n昏以為期、明星晢晢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">141.  墓門\n墓門有棘、斧以斯之。\n夫也不良、國人知之。\n知而不已、誰昔然矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>墓門有梅、有鴞萃止。\n夫也不良、歌以訊之。\n訊予不顧、顛倒思予。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">142.  防有鵲巢\n防有鵲巢、邛有旨苕。\n誰侜予美、心焉忉忉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>中唐有甓、邛有旨鷊。\n誰侜予美、心焉惕惕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">143.  月出\n月出皎兮、佼人僚兮。\n舒窈糾兮、勞心悄兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>月出皓兮、佼人懰兮。\n舒懮受兮、勞心慅兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>月出照兮、佼人燎兮。\n舒夭紹兮、勞心慘兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">144.  株林\n胡為乎株林、從夏南。\n匪適株林、從夏南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>駕我乘馬、說于株野。\n乘我乘駒、朝食于株。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">145.  澤陂\n彼澤之陂、有蒲與荷。\n有美一人、傷如之何。\n寤寐無為、涕泗滂沱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼澤之陂、有蒲與蕑。\n有美一人、碩大且卷。\n寤寐無為、中心悁悁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼澤之陂、有蒲菡萏。\n有美一人、碩大且儼。\n寤寐無為、 輾轉伏枕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">檜風\n146.  羔裘\n羔裘逍遙、狐裘以朝。\n豈不爾思、勞心忉忉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>羔裘翱翔、狐裘在堂。\n豈不爾思、我心憂傷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>羔裘如膏、日出有曜。\n豈不爾思、中心是悼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">147.  素冠\n庶見素冠兮、棘人欒欒兮、勞心慱慱兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>庶見素衣兮、我心傷悲兮、聊與子同歸兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>庶見素韡兮、我心蘊結兮、聊與子如一兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">148.  隰有萇楚\n隰有萇楚、猗儺其枝。\n夭之沃沃、樂子之無知。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>隰有萇楚、猗儺其華。\n夭之沃沃、樂子之無家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>隰有萇楚、猗儺其實。\n夭之沃沃、樂子之無室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">149.  匪風\n匪風發兮、匪車偈兮、顧瞻周道、中心怛兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>匪風飄兮、匪車嘌兮。\n顧瞻周道、中心弔兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誰能亨魚、溉之釜鬵。\n誰將西歸、懷之好音。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">曹風\n150.  蜉蝣\n蜉蝣之羽、衣裳楚楚。\n心之憂矣、於我歸處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蜉蝣之翼、采采衣服。\n心之憂矣、於我歸息。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蜉蝣掘閱、麻衣如雪。\n心之憂矣、於我歸說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">151.  候人\n彼候人兮、何戈與祋。\n彼其之子、三百赤芾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維鵜在梁、不濡其翼。\n彼其之子、不稱其服。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維鵜在梁、不濡其咮。\n彼其之子、不遂其媾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>薈兮蔚兮、南山朝隮。\n婉兮孌兮、季女斯飢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">152.  鳲鳩\n鳲鳩在桑、其子七兮。\n淑人君子、其儀一兮。\n其儀一兮、心如結兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳲鳩在桑、其子在梅。\n淑人君子、其帶伊絲。\n其帶伊絲、其弁伊騏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳲鳩在桑、其子在棘。\n淑人君子、其儀不忒。\n其儀不忒、正是四國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳲鳩在桑、其子在榛。\n淑人君子、正是國人。\n正是國人、胡不萬年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">153.  下泉\n冽彼下泉、浸彼苞稂。\n愾我寤嘆、念彼周京。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>冽彼下泉、浸彼苞蕭。\n愾我寤嘆、念彼京周。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>冽彼下泉、浸彼苞著。\n愾無寤歎、念彼京師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>芃芃黍苗、陰雨膏之。\n四國有王、郇伯勞之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">豳風\n154.  七月\n七月流火、九月授衣。\n一之日觱發、二之日栗烈。\n無衣無褐、何以卒歲。\n三之日于耜、四之日舉趾。\n同我婦子、饁彼南畝、田畯至喜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>七月流火、九月授衣。\n春日載陽、有鳴倉庚。\n女執懿筐、遵彼微行、爰求柔桑。\n春日遲遲、采蘩祁祁。\n女心傷悲、殆及公子同歸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>七月流火、八月萑葦。\n蠶月條桑、取彼斧斨、以伐遠揚、猗彼女桑。\n七月鳴鵙、八月載績。\n載玄載黃、我朱孔陽、為公子裳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四月秀葽、五月鳴蜩。\n八月其穫、十月隕蘀。\n一之日于貉、取彼狐狸、為公子裘。\n二之日其同、載纘武功、言私其豵、獻豜于公。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>五月斯螽動股、六月莎雞振羽。\n七月在野、八月在宇、九月在戶。\n十月蟋蟀、入我床下。\n穹窒熏鼠。\n塞向墐戶。\n嗟我婦子、曰為改歲、入此室處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>六月食鬱及薁、七月亨葵及菽。\n八月剝棗、十月穫稻。\n為此春酒、以介眉壽。\n七月食瓜、八月斷壺、九月叔苴、采荼薪樗。\n食我農夫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>九月築場圃、十月納禾稼。\n黍稷重穋、禾麻菽麥。\n嗟我農夫、我稼既同、上入執宮功。\n晝爾于茅、宵爾索綯。\n亟其乘屋、其始播百穀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>二之日鑿冰沖沖、三之日納于凌陰。\n四之日其蚤、獻羔祭韭。\n九月肅霜、十月滌場。\n朋酒斯響、曰殺羔羊。\n躋彼公堂、稱彼兕觥、萬壽無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">155.  鴟鴞\n鴟鴞鴟鴞、既取我子、無毀我室。\n恩斯勤斯、鬻子之閔斯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>迨天之未陰雨、徹彼桑土、綢繆牖戶。\n今女下民、或敢侮予。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>予手拮据、予所捋荼、予所蓄租、予口卒瘏、曰予未有室家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>予羽譙譙、予尾翛翛、予室翹翹、風雨所漂搖、予維音嘵嘵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">156.  東山\n我徂東山、慆慆不歸。\n我來自東、零雨其濛。\n我東曰歸、我心西悲。\n制彼裳衣、勿士行枚。\n蜎蜎者蠋、烝在桑野。\n敦彼獨宿、亦在車下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我徂東山、慆慆不歸。\n我來自東、零雨其濛。\n果臝之實、亦施于宇。\n伊威在室、蠨蛸在戶。\n町曈鹿場、熠燿宵行。\n不可畏也、伊可懷也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我徂東山、慆慆不歸。\n我來自東、零雨其濛。\n鸛鳴于垤、婦歎于室。\n洒掃穹窒、我征聿至。\n有敦瓜苦、烝在栗薪。\n自我不見、于今三年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我徂東山、慆慆不歸。\n我來自東、零雨其濛。\n倉庚于飛、熠燿其羽。\n之子于歸、皇駁其馬。\n親結其縭、九十其儀。\n其新孔嘉、其舊如之何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">157.  破斧\n既破我斧、又缺我斨。\n周公東征、四國是皇。\n哀我人斯、亦孔之將。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>既破我斧、又缺我錡。\n周公東征、四國是吪。\n哀我人斯、亦孔之嘉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>既破我斧、又缺我銶。\n周公東征、四國是遒。\n哀我人斯、亦孔之休。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">158.  伐柯\n伐柯如何、匪斧不克。\n取妻如何、匪媒不得。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>伐柯伐柯、其則不遠。\n我覯之子、籩豆有踐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">159.  九罭\n九罭之魚、鱒魴。\n我覯之子、袞衣繡裳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴻飛遵渚、公歸無所、於女信處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴻飛遵陸、公歸不復、於女信宿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>是以有袞衣兮、無以我公歸兮、無使我心悲兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">160.  狼跋\n狼跋其胡、載疐其尾。\n公孫碩膚、赤舄几几。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>狼疐其尾、載跋其胡。\n公孫碩膚、德音不瑕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">小雅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鹿鳴之什\n161.  鹿鳴\n呦呦鹿鳴、食野之苹。\n我有嘉賓、鼓瑟吹笙。\n吹笙鼓簧、承筐是將。\n人之好我、示我行周。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>呦呦鹿鳴、食野之蒿。\n我有嘉賓、德音孔昭。\n視民不恌、君子是則是傚。\n我有旨酒、嘉賓式燕以敖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>呦呦鹿鳴、食野之芩。\n我有嘉賓、鼓瑟鼓琴。\n鼓瑟鼓琴、和樂且湛。\n我有旨酒、以嘉樂嘉賓之心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">162.  四牡\n四牡騑騑、周道倭遲。\n豈不懷歸、王事靡盬、我心傷悲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四牡騑騑、嘽嘽駱馬。\n豈不懷歸、王事靡盬、不遑啟處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>翩翩者鵻、載飛載下、集于苞栩。\n王事靡盬、不遑將父。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>翩翩者鵻、載飛載止、集于苞杞。\n王事靡盬、不遑將母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>駕彼四駱、載驟駸駸。\n豈不懷歸、是用作歌、將母來諗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">163.  皇皇者華\n皇皇者華、于彼原隰。\n駪駪征夫、每懷靡及。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我馬維駒、六轡如濡。\n載馳載驅、周爰咨諏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我馬維騏、六轡如絲。\n載馳載驅、周爰咨謀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我馬維駱、六轡沃若。\n載馳載驅、周爰咨度。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我馬維駰、六轡既均。\n載馳載驅、周爰咨詢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">164.  常棣\n常棣之華、鄂不韡韡。\n凡今之人、莫如兄弟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>死喪之威、兄弟孔懷。\n原隰裒矣、兄弟求矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>脊今在原、兄弟急難。\n每有良朋、況也永歎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>兄弟鬩于牆、外禦其務。\n每有良朋、烝也無戎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>喪亂既平、既安且寧。\n雖有兄弟、不如友生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>儐爾籩豆、飲酒之飫。\n兄弟既具、和樂且孺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>妻子好合、如鼓瑟琴。\n兄弟既翕、和樂且湛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>宜爾室家、樂爾妻帑。\n是究是圖、亶其然乎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">165.  伐木\n伐木丁丁、鳥鳴嚶嚶。\n出自幽谷、遷于喬木。\n嚶其鳴矣、求其友聲。\n相彼鳥矣、猶求友聲。\n矧伊人矣、不求友生。\n神之聽之、終和且平。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>伐木許許、釃酒有藇。\n既有肥羜、以速諸父。\n寧適不來、微我弗顧。\n於粲洒掃、陳饋八簋。\n既有肥牡、以速諸舅。\n寧適不來、微我有咎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>伐木于阪、釃酒有衍。\n籩豆有踐、兄弟無遠。\n民之失德、乾餱以愆。\n有酒湑我、無酒酤我。\n坎坎鼓我、蹲蹲舞我。\n迨我暇矣、飲此湑矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">166.  天保\n天保定爾、亦孔之固。\n俾爾單厚、何福不除。\n俾爾多益、以莫不庶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天保定爾、俾爾戩穀。\n罄無不宜、受天百祿。\n降爾遐福、維日不足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天保定爾、以莫不興。\n如山如阜、如岡如陵。\n如川之方至、以莫不增。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>吉蠲為饎、是用孝享。\n禴祠烝嘗、于公先王。\n君曰卜爾、萬壽無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>神之弔矣、詒爾多福。\n民之質矣、日用飲食。\n群黍百姓、邊為爾德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>如月之恒、如日之升。\n如南山之壽、不騫不崩。\n如松伯之茂、無不爾或承。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">167.  采薇\n采薇采薇、薇亦作止。\n曰歸曰歸、歲亦莫止。\n靡室靡家、玁狁之故。\n不遑啟居、玁狁之故。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>采薇采薇、薇亦柔止。\n曰歸曰歸、心亦憂止。\n憂心烈烈、載飢載渴。\n我戌未定、靡使歸聘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>采薇采薇、薇亦剛止。\n曰歸曰歸、歲亦陽止。\n王事靡盬、不遑啟處。\n憂心孔疚、我行不來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>駕彼四牡、四牡騤騤。\n君子所依、小人所腓。\n四牡翼翼、象弭魚服。\n豈不日戒、玁狁孔亟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼爾維何、維常之華。\n彼路斯何、君子之車。\n戎車既駕、四牡業業。\n豈敢定居、一月三捷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>駕彼四牡、四牡騤騤。\n君子所依、小人所腓。\n四牡翼翼、象弭魚服。\n豈不日戒、玁狁孔亟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昔我往矣、楊柳依依。\n今我來思、雨雪靡靡。\n行道遲遲、載渴載飢。\n我心傷悲、莫知我哀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">168.  出車\n我出我車、于彼牧矣。\n自天子所、謂我來矣。\n召彼僕夫、謂之載矣。\n王事多難、維其棘矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我出我車、于彼郊矣。\n設此旐矣、建彼旄矣。\n彼旟旐斯、胡不旆旆。\n憂心悄悄、僕夫況瘁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王命南仲、往城于方。\n出車彭彭、旂旐央央。\n天子命我、城彼朔方。\n赫赫南仲、玁狁于襄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昔我往矣、黍稷方華。\n今我來思、雨雪載塗。\n王事多難、不遑啟居。\n豈不懷歸、畏此簡書。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>喓喓草虫、趯趯阜螽。\n未見君子、憂心忡忡。\n既見君子、我心則降。\n赫赫南仲、薄伐西戎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>春日遲遲、卉木萋萋。\n倉庚喈喈、采蘩祁祁。\n執訊獲醜、薄言還歸。\n赫赫南仲、玁狁于夷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">169.  杕杜\n有杕之杜、有睆其實。\n王事靡盬、繼嗣我日。\n日月陽止、女心傷止、征夫遑止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有杕之杜、其葉萋萋。\n王事靡盬、我心傷悲。\n卉木萋止、女心悲止、征夫歸止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼北山、言采其杞。\n王事靡盬、憂我父母。\n檀車幝幝、四牡痯痯、征夫不遠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>匪載匪來、憂心孔疚。\n期逝不至、而多為恤。\n卜筮偕止、會言近止、征夫邇止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">南陔\n笙詩無辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>白華之什\n白華\n笙詩無辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">華黍\n笙詩無辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">170.  魚麗\n魚麗于罶、鱨鯊。\n君子有酒、旨且多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>魚麗于罶、魴鱧。\n君子有酒、多且旨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>魚麗于罶、鰋鯉。\n君子有酒、旨且有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>物其多矣、維其嘉矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>物其旨矣、維其偕矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>物其有矣、維其時矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">由庚\n笙詩無辭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">171.  南有嘉魚\n南有嘉魚、烝然罩罩。\n君子有酒、嘉賓式燕以樂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南有嘉魚、烝然汕汕。\n君子有酒、嘉賓式燕以衎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南有樛木、 甘瓠纍之。\n君子有酒、嘉賓式燕綏之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>翩翩者鵻、烝然來思。\n君子有酒、嘉賓式燕又思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">崇丘\n笙詩無辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">172.  南山有臺\n南山有臺、北山有萊。\n樂只君子、邦家之基。\n樂只君子、萬壽無期。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南山有桑、北山有楊。\n樂只君子、邦家之光。\n樂只君子、萬壽無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南山有杞、北山有李。\n樂只君子、民之父母。\n樂只君子、德音不已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南山有栲、北山有杻。\n樂只君子、遐不眉壽。\n樂只君子、德音是茂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南山有枸、北山有楰。\n樂只君子、遐不黃耇。\n樂只君子、保艾爾後。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">由儀\n無辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">173.  蓼蕭\n蓼彼蕭斯、零露湑兮。\n既見君子、我心寫兮。\n燕笑語兮、是以有譽處兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蓼彼蕭斯、零露瀼瀼。\n既見君子、為龍為光。\n其德不爽、壽考不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蓼彼蕭斯、零露泥泥。\n既見君子、孔燕豈弟。\n宜兄宜弟、令德壽豈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蓼彼蕭斯、零露濃濃。\n既見君子、鞗革沖沖。\n和鸞雝雝、萬福攸同。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">174.  湛露\n湛湛露斯、匪陽不晞。\n厭厭夜飲、不醉無歸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>湛湛露斯、在彼豐草。\n厭厭夜飲、在宗載考。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>湛湛露斯、在彼杞棘。\n顯允君子、莫不令德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其實其椅、其實離離。\n豈弟君子、莫不令儀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">彤弓之什\n175.  彤弓\n彤弓弨兮、受言藏之。\n我有嘉賓、中心貺之。\n鐘鼓既設、一朝饗之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彤弓弨兮、受言載之。\n我有嘉賓、中心喜之。\n鐘鼓既設、一朝右之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彤弓弨兮、受言櫜之。\n我有嘉賓、中心好之。\n鐘鼓既設、一朝酬之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">176.  菁菁者莪\n菁菁者莪、在彼中阿。\n既見君子、樂且有儀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>菁菁者莪、在彼中沚。\n既見君子、我心則喜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>菁菁者莪、在彼中陵。\n既見君子、錫我百朋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>汎汎楊舟、載沉載浮。\n既見君子、我心則休。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">177.  六月\n六月棲棲、戎車既飭。\n四牡騤騤、載是常服。\n玁狁孔熾、我是用急。\n王于出征、以匡王國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>比物四驪、閑之維則。\n維此六月、既成我服。\n我服既成、于三十里。\n王于出征、以佐天子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四牡脩廣、其大有顒。\n薄伐玁狁、以奏膚公。\n有嚴有翼、共武之服。\n共武之服、以定王國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>玁狁匪茹、整居焦穫。\n侵鎬及方、至于涇陽。\n織文鳥章、白旆央央。\n元戎十乘、以先啟行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>戎車既安、如輊如軒。\n四牡既佶、既佶且閑。\n薄伐玁狁、至于大原。\n文武吉甫、萬邦為憲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>吉甫燕喜、既多受祉。\n來歸自鎬、我行永久。\n飲御諸友、炰鱉膾鯉。\n侯誰在矣、張仲孝友。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">178.  采芑\n薄言采芑、于彼新田、于此菑畝。\n方叔蒞止、其車三千、師干之試。\n方叔率止、乘其四騏、四騏翼翼。\n路車有奭、簟笰魚服、鉤膺鞗革。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>薄言采芑、于彼新田、于此中鄉。\n方叔蒞止、其車三千、旂旐央央。\n方叔率止、約軝錯衡、八鸞瑲瑲。\n服其命服、朱芾斯皇、有瑲蔥珩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴥彼飛隼、其飛戾天、亦集爰止。\n方叔蒞止、其車三千、師干之試。\n方叔率止、鉦人伐鼓、陳師鞠旅。\n顯允方叔、伐鼓淵淵、振旅闐闐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蠢爾蠻荊、大邦為讎。\n方叔元老、克壯其猶。\n方叔率止、執訊獲醜。\n戎車嘽嘽、嘽嘽焞焞、如霆如雷。\n顯允方叔、征伐玁狁、蠻荊來威。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">179.  車攻\n我車既攻、我馬既同。\n四牡龐龐、駕言徂東。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>田車既好、四牡孔阜。\n東有甫草、駕言行狩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>之子于苗、選徒囂囂。\n建旐設旄、搏獸于敖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>駕彼四牡、四牡奕奕。\n赤芾金舄、會同有繹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>決拾既佽、弓矢既調。\n射夫既同、助我舉柴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四黃既駕、兩驂不猗。\n不失其馳、舍矢如破。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蕭蕭馬鳴、悠悠旆旌。\n徒御不驚、大庖不盈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>之子于征、有聞無聲。\n允矣君子、展也大成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">180.  吉日\n吉日維戊、既伯既禱。\n田車既好、四牡孔阜。\n升彼大阜、從其群醜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>吉日庚午、既差我馬。\n獸之所同、麀鹿麌麌。\n漆沮子從、天子之所。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼中原、其祁孔有。\n儦儦俟俟、或群或友。\n悉率左右、以燕天子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>既張我弓、既挾我矢。\n發彼小豝、殪此大兕。\n以御賓客、且以酌醴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">181.  鴻雁\n鴻雁于飛、肅肅其羽。\n之子于征、劬勞于野。\n爰及矜人、哀此鰥寡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴻雁于飛、集于中澤。\n之子于垣、百堵皆作。\n雖則劬勞、其究安宅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴻雁于飛、哀鳴嗷嗷。\n維此哲人、謂我劬勞。\n維彼愚人、謂我宣驕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">182.  庭燎\n夜如何其、夜未央、庭燎之光。\n君子至止、鸞聲將將。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>夜如何其、夜未艾、庭燎晢晢。\n君子至止、鸞聲噦噦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>夜如何其、夜鄉晨、庭燎有輝。\n君子至止、言觀其旂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">183.  沔水\n沔彼流誰、朝宗于海。\n鴥彼飛隼、載飛載止。\n嗟我兄弟、邦人諸友、莫肯念亂、誰無父母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>沔彼流水、其流湯湯。\n鴥彼飛隼、載飛載揚。\n念彼不蹟、載起載行。\n心之憂矣、不可弭忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴥彼飛隼、率彼中陵。\n民之訛言、寧莫之懲。\n我友敬矣、讒言其興。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">184.  鶴鳴\n鶴鳴于九皋、聲聞于野。\n魚潛在淵、或在于渚。\n樂彼之園、爰有樹檀、其下維蘀。\n它山之石、可以為錯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鶴鳴于九皋、聲聞于天。\n魚在于渚、或潛在淵。\n樂彼之園、爰有樹檀、其下維?c。\n它山之石、可以攻玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">祈父之什\n185.  祈父\n祈父、予王之爪牙。\n胡轉予于恤、靡所止居。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>祈父、予王之爪士。\n胡轉予于恤、靡所底止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>祈父、亶不聰。\n胡轉予于恤、有母之尸饔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">186.  白駒\n皎皎白駒、食我場苗。\n縶之維之、以永今朝。\n所謂伊人、於焉逍遙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>皎皎白駒、食我場藿。\n縶之維之、以永今夕。\n所謂伊人、於焉嘉客。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>皎皎白駒、賁然來思。\n爾公爾侯、逸豫無期。\n慎爾優遊、勉爾遁思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>皎皎白駒、在彼空谷。\n生芻一束、其人如玉。\n毋金玉爾音、而有遐心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">187.  黃鳥\n黃鳥黃鳥。\n無集于穀。\n無啄無粟。\n此邦之人。\n不我肯穀。\n言旋言歸。\n復我邦族。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>黃鳥黃鳥。\n無集于桑。\n無啄我粱。\n此邦之人。\n不可與明。\n言旋言歸。\n復我諸兄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>黃鳥黃鳥。\n無集于栩。\n無啄我黍。\n此邦之人。\n不可與處。\n言旋言歸。\n復我諸父。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">188.  我行其野\n我行其野、蔽芾其樗。\n婚姻之故、言就爾居。\n爾不我畜、復我邦家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我行其野、言采其蓫。\n婚姻之故、言就爾宿。\n爾不我畜、言歸思復。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我行其野、言采其葍。\n不思舊姻、求爾新特。\n成不以富、亦祇以異。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">189.  斯干\n秩秩斯干、幽幽南山。\n如竹苞矣、如松茂矣。\n兄及弟矣、式相好矣、無相猶矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>似續妣祖、築室百堵、西南其戶。\n爰居爰處、爰笑爰語。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>約之閣閣、椓之橐橐。\n風雨攸除、鳥鼠攸去、君子攸芋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>如跂斯翼、如矢斯棘、如鳥斯革。\n如翬斯飛、君子攸躋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>殖殖其庭、有覺其楹、噲噲其正、噦噦其冥、君子攸寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>下莞上簟、乃安斯寢。\n乃寢乃興、乃占我夢。\n吉夢維何、維熊維羆、 維虺維蛇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>大人占之。\n維熊維羆、男子之祥。\n維虺維蛇、女子之祥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乃生男子、載寢之床、載衣之裳、載弄之璋。\n其泣喤喤、朱芾斯皇、室家君王。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乃生女子、載寢之地、載衣之裼、 載弄之瓦。\n無非無儀、唯酒食是議、無父母詒罹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">190.  無羊\n誰謂爾無羊、三百維群。\n誰謂爾無牛、九十其犉。\n爾羊來思、其角濈濈。\n爾牛來思、其耳濕濕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>或降于阿、或飲于池、或寢于訛。\n爾牧來思、何蓑何笠、或負其餱。\n三十維物、爾牲則具。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爾牧來思、以薪以蒸、以雌以雄。\n爾羊來思、矜矜兢兢、不騫不崩。\n麾之以肱、畢來既升。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>牧人乃夢、眾維魚矣、旐維旟矣。\n大人占之、眾維魚矣、實維豐年。\n旐維旟矣、室家溱溱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">191.  節南山\n節彼南山、維石巖巖。\n赫赫師尹、民具爾瞻。\n憂心如惔、不敢戲談。\n國既卒斬、何用不監。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>節彼南山、有實其猗。\n赫赫師尹、不平謂何。\n天方薦瘥、喪亂弘多。\n民言無嘉、憯莫懲嗟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>尹氏大師、維周之氏。\n秉國之均、四方是維。\n天子是毗、俾民不迷。\n不弔昊天、不宜空我師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>弗躬弗親、庶民弗信。\n弗問弗仕、勿罔君子。\n式夷式已、無小人殆。\n瑣瑣姻亞、則無膴仕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昊天不傭、降此鞠 。\n昊天不惠、降此大戾。\n君子如屆、俾民心闋。\n君子如夷、惡怒是違。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>不弔昊天、亂靡有定。\n式月斯生、俾民不寧。\n憂心如酲、誰秉國成。\n不自為政、卒勞百姓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>駕彼四牡、四牡項領。\n我瞻四方、蹙蹙靡所騁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>方茂爾惡、相爾矛矣。\n既夷既懌、如相酬矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昊天不平、我王不寧。\n不懲其心、覆怨其正。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>家父作誦、以究王  。\n式訛爾心、以畜萬邦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">192.  正月\n正月繁霜、我心憂傷。\n民之訛言、亦孔之將。\n念我獨兮、憂心京京。\n哀我小心、癙憂以痒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>父母生我、胡俾我瘉。\n不自我先、不自我後。\n好言自口、莠言自口。\n憂心愈愈、是以有侮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>憂心惸惸、念我無祿。\n民之無辜、并其臣僕。\n哀我人斯、于何從祿。\n瞻烏爰止、于誰之屋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼中林、侯薪猴蒸。\n民今方殆、視天夢夢。\n既克有定、靡人弗勝。\n有皇上帝、伊誰云憎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>謂山蓋卑、為岡為陵。\n民之訛言、寧莫之懲。\n召彼故老、訊之占夢。\n具曰予聖、誰知烏之雌雄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>謂天蓋高、不敢不局。\n謂地蓋厚、不敢不蹐。\n維號斯言、有倫有脊。\n哀今之人、胡為虺蜴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼阪田、有菀其特。\n天之扤我、如不我克。\n彼求我則、如不我得。\n執我仇仇、亦不我力。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>心之憂矣、如或結之。\n今茲之正、胡然厲矣。\n燎之方揚、寧或滅之。\n赫赫周宗、褒姒滅之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>終其永懷、又窘陰雨。\n其車既載、乃棄爾輔。\n載輸爾載、 將伯助予。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>無棄爾輔、員于爾輻。\n屢顧爾僕、不輸爾載。\n終踰絕險、曾是不意。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>魚在于沼、亦匪克樂。\n潛雖伏矣、亦孔之炤。\n憂心慘慘、念國之為虐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼有旨酒、又有嘉殽。\n洽比其鄰、昏姻孔云。\n念我獨兮、憂心慇慇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>佌佌彼有屋、蔌蔌方有穀。\n民今之無祿、天夭是椓。\n哿矣富人、哀此惸獨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">193.  十月之交\n十月之交、朔日辛卯。\n日有食之、亦孔之醜。\n彼月而微、此日而微。\n今此下民、亦孔之哀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>日月告凶、不用其行。\n四國無政、不用其良。\n彼月而食、則維其常。\n此日而食、于何不臧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>燁燁震電、不寧不令。\n百川沸騰、山冢崒崩。\n高岸為谷、深谷為陵。\n哀今之人、胡憯莫懲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>皇父卿士。\n番維司徒。\n家伯維宰。\n仲允膳夫。\n棸子內史。\n蹶維趣馬。\n楀維師氏。\n豔妻煽方處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>抑此皇父、豈曰不時。\n胡為我作、不即我謀。\n徹我牆屋、田卒汙萊。\n曰予不戕、禮則然矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>皇父孔聖、作都于向。\n擇三有事、亶侯多藏。\n不憖遺一老、俾守我王。\n擇有車馬、以居徂向。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>黽勉從事、不敢告勞。\n無罪無辜、讒口囂囂。\n下民之孽、匪降自天。\n噂沓背憎、職競由人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>悠悠我里、亦孔之痗。\n四方有羨、我獨居憂。\n民莫不逸、我獨不敢休。\n天命不徹、我不敢傚我友自逸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">194.  雨無正\n浩浩昊天、不駿其德。\n降喪飢饉、斬伐四國。\n旻天疾威、弗盧弗圖。\n舍彼有罪、既伏其辜。\n若此無罪、淪胥以鋪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>周宗既滅、靡所止戾。\n正大夫離居、莫知我勩。\n三事大夫、莫肯夙夜。\n邦君諸侯、莫肯朝夕。\n庶曰式臧、覆出為惡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>如何昊天。\n辟言不信。\n如彼行邁、則靡所臻。\n凡百君子、各敬爾身。\n胡不相畏、不畏于天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>戎成不退、飢成不遂。\n曾我御、憯憯日瘁。\n凡百君子、莫肯用訊。\n聽言則答、譖言則退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>哀哉不能言、匪舌是出、維躬是瘁。\n哿矣能言、巧言如流、俾躬處休。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維曰于仕、孔棘且殆。\n云不可使、得罪于天子。\n亦云可使、怨及朋友。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>謂爾遷于王都、曰予未有室家。\n鼠思泣血、無言不疾。\n昔爾出居、誰從作爾室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">小旻之什\n195.  小旻\n旻天疾威、敷于下土。\n謀猶回遹、何日斯沮。\n謀臧不從、不臧覆用。\n我視謀猶、亦孔之邛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>潝潝訿訿、亦孔之哀。\n謀之其臧、則具是違。\n謀之不臧、則具是依。\n我視謀猶、伊于胡底。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我龜既厭、不我告猶。\n謀夫孔多、是用不集。\n發言盈庭、誰敢執其咎。\n如匪行邁謀、是用不得于道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>哀哉為猶、匪先民是程、匪大猶是經、維邇言是聽、維邇言是爭。\n如彼築室于道謀、是用不潰于成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>國雖靡止、或聖或否。\n民雖靡膴、或哲或謀、或肅或艾。\n如彼泉流、無淪胥以敗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>不敢暴虎、不敢馮河。\n人知其一、莫知其它。\n戰戰兢兢、如臨深淵、如履薄冰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">196.  小宛\n宛彼鳴鳩、翰飛戾天。\n我心憂傷、念昔先人。\n明發不寐、有懷二人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>人之齊聖、飲酒溫克。\n彼昏不知、壹醉日富。\n各敬爾儀、天命不又。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>中原有菽、庶民采之。\n螟蛉有子、蜾蠃負之。\n教誨爾子、式穀似之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>題彼脊令、載飛載鳴。\n我日斯邁、而月斯征。\n夙興夜寐、無忝爾所生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>交交桑扈、率場啄粟。\n哀我填寡、宜岸宜獄。\n握粟出卜、自何能穀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>溫溫恭人、如集于木。\n惴惴小心、如臨于谷。\n戰戰兢兢、如履薄冰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">197.  小弁\n弁彼鸒斯、歸飛提提。\n民莫不穀、我獨于罹。\n何辜于天、我罪伊何。\n心之憂矣、云如之何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>踧踧周道、鞫為茂草。\n我心憂傷、惄焉如擣。\n假寐永嘆、維憂用老。\n心之憂矣、疢如疾首。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維桑與梓、必恭敬止。\n靡瞻匪父、靡依匪母。\n不屬于毛、不離于裹。\n天之生我、我辰安在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>菀彼柳斯、鳴蜩嘒嘒。\n有凗者淵、萑葦淠淠。\n譬彼舟流、不知所屆。\n心之憂矣、不遑假寐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鹿斯之奔、維足伎伎。\n雉之朝雊、尚求其雌。\n譬彼壞木、疾用無枝。\n心之憂矣、寧莫之知。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>相彼投兔、尚或先之。\n行有死人、尚或墐之。\n君子秉心、維其忍之。\n心之憂矣、涕既隕之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>君子信讒、如或酬之。\n君子不惠、不舒究之。\n伐木掎矣、析薪杝矣。\n舍彼有罪、予之佗矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>莫高匪山、莫浚匪泉。\n君子無易由言、耳屬于垣。\n無逝我梁、無發我笱。\n我躬不閱、遑恤我後。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">198.  巧言\n悠悠昊天、曰父母且。\n無罪無辜、亂如此憮。\n昊天已威、予慎無罪。\n昊天泰憮、予慎無辜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>亂之初生、僭始既涵。\n亂之又生、君子信讒。\n君子如怒、亂庶遄沮。\n君子如祉、亂庶遄已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>君子屢盟、亂是用長。\n君子信盜、亂是用暴。\n盜言孔甘、亂是用餤。\n匪其止共、維王之邛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>奕奕寢廟、君子作之。\n秩秩大猷、聖人莫之。\n他人有心、予忖度之。\n躍躍毚兔、遇犬獲之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>荏染柔木、君子樹之。\n往來行言、心焉數之。\n蛇蛇碩言、出自口矣。\n巧言如簧、顏之厚矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼何人斯、居河之麋。\n無拳無勇、職為亂階。\n既微且尰、爾勇伊何。\n為猶將多、爾居徒幾何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">199.  何人斯\n彼何人斯、其心孔艱。\n胡逝我梁、不入我門。\n伊誰云從、維暴之云。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>二人從行、誰為此禍。\n胡逝我梁、不入唁我。\n始者不如今、云不我可。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼何人斯、胡逝我陳。\n我聞其聲、不見其身。\n不愧于人、不畏于天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼何人斯、其為飄風。\n胡不自北、胡不自南。\n胡逝我梁、祇攪我心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爾之安行、亦不遑舍。\n爾之亟行、遑脂爾車。\n壹者之來、云何其盱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爾還而入、我心易也。\n還而不入、否難知也。\n壹者之來、俾我祇也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>伯氏吹壎、仲氏吹篪。\n及爾如貫、諒不我知。\n出此三物、以詛爾斯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>為鬼為蜮、則不可得。\n有靦面目、視人罔極。\n作此好歌、以極反側。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">200.  巷伯\n萋兮斐兮、成是貝錦。\n彼譖人者、亦已大甚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>哆兮侈兮、成是南箕。\n彼譖人者、誰適與謀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>緝緝翩翩、謀欲譖人。\n慎爾言也、謂爾不信。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>捷捷幡幡、謀欲譖言。\n豈不爾受、既其女遷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>驕人好好、勞人草草。\n蒼天蒼天、視彼驕人、矜此勞人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼譖人者、誰適與謀。\n取彼譖人、投畀豺虎。\n豺虎不食、投畀有北。\n有北不受、投畀有昊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>楊園之道、猗于畝丘。\n寺人孟子、作為此詩。\n凡百君子、敬而聽之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">201.  谷風\n習習谷風、維風及雨。\n將恐將懼、維予與女。\n將安將樂、女轉棄予。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>習習谷風、維風及頹。\n將恐將懼、寘予于懷。\n將安將樂、棄予如遺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>習習谷風、維山崔嵬。\n無草不死、無木不萎。\n忘我大德、思我小怨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">202.  蓼莪\n蓼蓼者莪、匪莪伊蒿。\n哀哀父母、生我劬勞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蓼蓼者莪、匪莪伊蔚。\n哀哀父母、生我勞瘁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>缾之罊矣、維罍之恥。\n鮮民之生、不如死之久矣。\n無父何怙、無母何恃。\n出則銜恤、入則靡至。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>父兮生我、母兮鞠我。\n拊我畜我、長我育我。\n顧我復我、出入腹我。\n欲報之德、昊天罔極。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南山烈烈、飄風發發。\n民莫不穀、我獨何害。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>南山律律、飄風弗弗。\n民莫不穀、我獨不卒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">203.  大東\n有饛簋飧、有捄棘匕。\n周道如砥、其直如矢。\n君子所履、小人所視。\n睠言顧之、潸焉出涕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>小東大東、杼柚其空。\n糾糾葛屨、可以履霜。\n佻佻公子、行彼周行。\n既往既來、使我心疚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有冽氿泉、 無浸穫薪。\n契契寤歎、哀我憚人。\n薪是穫薪、尚可載也。\n哀我憚人、亦可息也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>東人之子、職勞不來。\n西人之子、粲粲衣服。\n舟人之子、熊羆是裘。\n私人之子、百僚是試。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>或以其酒、不以其漿。\n鞙鞙佩璲、不以其長。\n維天有漢、監亦有光。\n跂彼織女、終日七襄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>雖則七襄、不成報章。\n睆彼牽牛、不以服箱。\n東有啟明、西有長庚。\n有捄天畢、載施之行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維南有箕、不可以簸揚。\n維北有斗、不可以挹酒漿。\n維南有箕、載翕其舌。\n維北有斗、西柄之揭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">204.  四月\n四月維夏、六月徂暑。\n先祖匪人、胡寧忍予。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>秋日淒淒、百卉具腓。\n亂離瘼矣、爰其適歸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>冬日烈烈、飄風發發。\n民莫不穀、我獨何害。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有嘉卉、侯栗侯梅。\n廢為殘賊、莫知其尤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>相彼泉水、載清載濁。\n我曰構禍、曷云能穀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>滔滔江漢、南國之紀。\n盡瘁以仕、寧莫我有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>匪鷻匪鳶、翰飛戾天。\n匪鱣匪鮪、潛逃于淵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>山有蕨薇、隰有杞桋。\n君子作歌、維以告哀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">北山之什\n205.  北山\n涉彼北山、言采其杞。\n偕偕士子、朝夕從事。\n王事靡盬、憂我父母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>溥天之下、莫非王土。\n率土之濱、莫非王臣。\n大夫不均、我從事獨賢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四牡彭彭、王事傍傍。\n嘉我未老、鮮我方將。\n旅力方剛、經營四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>或燕燕居息、或盡瘁事國。\n或息偃在床、或不已于行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>或不知叫號、或慘慘劬勞。\n或棲遲偃仰、或王事鞅掌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>或湛樂飲酒、或慘慘畏咎。\n或出入風議、或靡事不為。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">206.  無將大車\n無將大車、祇自塵兮。\n無思百憂、祇自疧兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>無將大車、維塵冥冥。\n無思百憂、不出于熲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>無將大車、維塵雝兮。\n無思百憂、祇自重兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">207.  小明\n明明上天、照臨下土。\n我征徂西、至于艽野。\n二月初吉、載離寒暑。\n心之憂矣、其毒大苦。\n念彼共人、涕零如雨。\n豈不懷歸、畏此罪罟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昔我往矣、日月方除。\n曷云其還、歲聿云莫。\n念我獨兮、我事孔庶。\n心之憂矣、憚我不暇。\n念彼共人、睠睠懷顧。\n豈不懷歸、畏此譴怒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昔我往矣、日月方奧。\n曷云其還、政事愈蹙。\n歲聿云莫、采蕭穫菽。\n心之憂矣、自始伊戚。\n念彼共人、興言出宿。\n豈不懷歸、畏此反覆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>嗟爾君子、無恆安處。\n靖共爾位、正直是興。\n神之聽之、式穀以女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>嗟爾君子、無恆安息。\n靖共爾位、好是正直。\n神之聽之、介爾景福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">208.  鼓鍾\n鼓鍾將將、淮水湯湯。\n憂心且傷。\n淑人君子、懷允不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鼓鍾喈喈、淮水湝湝。\n憂心且悲。\n淑人君子、其德不回。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鼓鍾伐鼛、淮有三洲。\n憂心且妯。\n淑人君子、其德不猶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鼓鍾欽欽、鼓瑟鼓琴。\n笙磬同音。\n以雅以南、以籥不偕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">209.  楚茨\n楚楚者茨、言抽其棘。\n自昔何為、我蓺黍稷。\n我黍與與、我稷翼翼。\n我倉既盈、我庾維憶。\n以為酒食、以饗以祀。\n以妥以侑、以介景福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>濟濟蹌蹌、絜爾牛羊、以往烝嘗。\n或剝或亨、或肆或將。\n祝祭于祊、祀事孔明。\n先祖是皇、神保是饗。\n孝孫有慶。\n報以介福、萬壽無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>執爨踖踖、為俎孔碩、或燔或炙。\n君婦莫莫、為豆孔庶。\n為賓為客、獻酬交錯。\n禮儀卒度、笑語卒獲。\n神保是格。\n報以介福、萬壽攸酢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我孔熯矣、式禮莫愆。\n工祝致告、徂賚孝孫。\n苾芬孝祀、神嗜飲食。\n卜爾百福、如幾如式。\n既齊既稷、既匡既敕。\n永錫爾極、時萬時憶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>禮儀既備、鍾鼓既戒。\n孝孫徂位、工祝致告。\n神具醉止、皇尸載起。\n鼓鍾送尸、神保聿歸。\n諸宰君婦、廢徹不遲。\n諸父兄弟、備言燕私。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>樂具入奏、以綏後祿。\n爾殽既將、莫怨具慶。\n既醉既飽、小大稽首。\n神嗜飲食、使君壽考。\n孔惠孔時、維其盡之。\n子子孫孫、勿替引之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">210.  信南山\n信彼南山、維禹甸之。\n畇畇原隰、曾孫田之。\n我疆我理、南東其畝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>上天同雲、雨雪雰雰。\n益之以霢霂、既優既渥、既霑既足、生我百穀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>疆場翼翼、黍稷彧彧。\n曾孫之穡、以為酒食。\n畀我尸賓、壽考萬年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>中田有廬、疆場有瓜。\n是剝是菹、獻之皇祖。\n曾孫壽考、受天之祜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>祭以清酒、從以騂牡、享于祖考。\n執其鸞刀、以啟其毛、取其血膋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>是烝是享、苾苾芬芬、祀事孔明。\n先祖是皇。\n報以介福、萬壽無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">211.  甫田\n倬彼甫田、歲取十千。\n我取其陳、食我農人。\n自古有年。\n今適南畝、或耘或耔、黍稷薿薿。\n攸介攸止、烝我髦士。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>以我齊明、與我犧羊、以社以方。\n我田既臧、農夫之慶。\n琴瑟擊鼓、以御田祖。\n以祈甘雨、以介我稷黍、以穀我士女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>曾孫來止、以其婦子、饁彼南畝、田畯至喜。\n攘其左右、嘗其旨否。\n禾易長畝、終善且有。\n曾孫不怒、農夫克敏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>曾孫之稼、如茨如梁。\n曾孫之庾、如坻如京。\n乃求千斯倉、乃求萬斯箱。\n黍稷稻梁、農夫之慶。\n報以介福、萬壽無疆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">212.  大田\n大田多稼、既種既戒。\n既備乃事、以我覃耜、俶載南畝、播厥百穀。\n既庭且碩、曾孫是若。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>既方既皁、既堅既好。\n不稂不莠、去其螟螣。\n及其蟊賊、無害我田稚。\n田祖有神、秉畀炎火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有渰萋萋、興雨祁祁。\n雨我公田、遂及我私。\n彼有不稚、此有不斂穧。\n彼有遺秉、此有滯穗、伊寡婦之利。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>曾孫來止、以其婦子。\n饁彼南畝、田畯至喜。\n來方禋祀、以其騂黑。\n與其黍稷、以享以祀。\n以介景福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">213.  瞻彼洛矣\n瞻彼洛矣、維水泱泱。\n君子至止、福祿如茨。\n韎韐有奭、以作六師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼洛矣、維水泱泱。\n君子至止、鞞琫有珌。\n君子萬年、保其家室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼洛矣、維水泱泱。\n君子至止、福祿既同。\n君子萬年、保其家邦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">214.  裳裳者華\n裳裳者華、其葉湑兮。\n我覯之子、我心寫兮。\n我心寫兮、是以有譽處兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>裳裳者華、芸其黃矣。\n我覯之子、維其有章矣。\n維其有章矣、是以有慶矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>裳裳者華、或黃或白。\n我覯之子、乘其四駱。\n乘其四駱、六轡沃若。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>左之左之、君子宜之。\n右之右之、君子有之。\n維其有之、是以似之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">桑扈之什\n215.  桑扈\n交交桑扈、有鶯其羽。\n君子樂胥、受天之祜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>交交桑扈、有鶯其領。\n君子樂胥、萬邦之屏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>之屏之翰、百辟為憲。\n不戢不難、受福不那。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>兕觥其觩、旨酒思柔。\n彼交匪敖、萬福來求。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">216.  鴛鴦\n鴛鴦于飛、畢之羅之。\n君子萬年、福祿宜之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴛鴦在梁、戢其左翼。\n君子萬年、宜其遐福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乘馬在廄、摧之秣之。\n君子萬年、福祿艾之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乘馬在廄、秣之摧之。\n君子萬年、福祿綏之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">217.  頍弁\n有頍者弁、實維伊何。\n爾酒既旨、爾殽既嘉。\n豈伊異人、兄弟匪他。\n蔦與女蘿、施于松柏。\n未見君子、憂心弈弈。\n既見君子、庶幾說懌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有頍者弁、實維何期。\n爾酒既旨、爾殽既時。\n豈伊異人、兄弟具來。\n蔦與女蘿、施于松上。\n未見君子、憂心怲怲。\n既見君子、庶幾有臧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有頍者弁、實維在首。\n爾酒既旨、爾殽既阜。\n豈伊異人、兄弟甥舅。\n如彼雨雪、先集維霰。\n死喪無日、無幾相見。\n樂酒今夕、君子維宴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">218.  車舝\n間關車之舝兮、思孌季女逝兮。\n匪飢匪渴、德音來括。\n雖無好友、式燕且喜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>依彼平林、有集維鷮。\n辰彼碩女、令德來教。\n式燕且譽、好爾無射。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>雖無旨酒、式飲庶幾。\n雖無嘉殽、式食庶幾。\n雖無德與女、式歌且舞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼高岡、析其柞薪。\n析其柞薪、其葉湑兮。\n鮮我覯爾、我心寫兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>高山仰止、景行行止。\n四牡騑騑、六轡如琴。\n覯爾新昏、以慰我心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">219.  青蠅\n營營青蠅、止于樊。\n豈弟君子、無信讒言。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>營營青蠅、止于棘。\n讒人罔機、交亂四國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>營營青蠅、止于榛。\n讒人罔機、構我二人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">220.  賓之初筵\n賓之初筵、左右秩秩。\n籩豆有楚、殽喝維旅。\n酒既和旨、飲酒孔偕。\n鐘鼓既設、舉酬逸逸。\n大侯既抗、弓矢斯張。\n射夫既同、獻爾發功。\n發彼有的、以祈爾爵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>籥舞笙鼓、樂既和奏。\n烝衎烈祖、以洽百禮。\n百禮既至、有壬有林。\n錫爾純嘏、子孫其湛。\n其湛曰樂、各奏爾能。\n賓載手仇、室人入又。\n酌彼康爵、以奏爾時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>賓之初筵、溫溫其恭。\n其未醉止、威儀反反。\n曰既醉止、威儀幡幡。\n舍其坐遷、屢舞僊僊。\n其未醉止、威儀抑抑。\n曰既醉止、威儀怭怭。\n是曰既醉、不知其秩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>賓既醉止、載號載呶。\n亂我籩豆、屢舞僛僛。\n是曰既醉、不知其郵。\n側弁之俄、屢舞傞傞。\n既醉而出、並受其福。\n醉而不出、是謂伐德。\n飲酒孔嘉、維其令儀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>凡此飲酒、或醉或否。\n既立之監、或佐之史。\n彼醉不臧、不醉反恥。\n式勿從謂、無俾大怠。\n匪言勿言、匪由勿語。\n由醉之言、俾出童羖。\n三爵不識、矧敢多又。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">221.  魚藻\n魚在在藻、有頒其首。\n王在在鎬、豈樂飲酒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>魚在在藻、有莘其尾。\n王在在鎬、飲酒樂豈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>魚在在藻、依于其蒲。\n王在在鎬、有那其居。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">222.  采菽\n采菽采菽、筐之筥之。\n君子來朝、何錫予之。\n雖無予之、路車乘馬。\n又何予之、玄袞及黼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>觱沸檻泉、言采其芹。\n君子來朝、言觀其旂。\n其旂淠淠、鸞聲嘒嘒。\n載驂載駟、君子所屆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>赤芾在股、邪幅在下。\n彼交匪紓、天子所予。\n樂只君子、天子命之。\n樂只君子、福祿申之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維柞之枝、其葉蓬蓬。\n樂只君子、殿天子之邦。\n樂只君子、萬福攸同。\n平平左右、亦是率從。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>汎汎楊舟、紼纚維之。\n樂只君子、天之葵之。\n樂只君子、福祿膍之。\n優哉游哉、亦是戾矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">223.  角弓\n騂騂角弓、翩其反矣。\n兄弟昏姻、無胥遠矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爾之遠矣、民胥然矣。\n爾之教矣、民胥傚矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>此令兄弟、綽綽有裕。\n不令兄弟、交相為瘉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>民之無良、相怨一方。\n受爵不讓、至于已斯亡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>老馬反為駒、不顧其後。\n如食宜饇、如酌孔取。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>毋教猱升木、如塗塗附。\n君子有徽猷、小人與屬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>雨雪瀌瀌、見晛曰消。\n莫肯下遺、式居婁驕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>雨雪浮浮、見晛曰流。\n如蠻如髦、我是用憂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">224.  菀柳\n有菀者柳、不尚息焉。\n上帝甚蹈、無自暱焉。\n俾予靖之、後予極焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有菀者柳、不尚愒焉。\n上帝甚蹈、無自瘵焉。\n俾予靖之、後予邁焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有鳥高飛、亦傅于天。\n彼人之心、于何其臻。\n曷予靖之、居以凶矜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">都人士之什\n225.  都人士\n彼都人士、狐裘黃黃。\n其容不改、出言有章。\n行歸于周、萬民所望。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼都人士、臺笠緇撮。\n彼君子女、綢直如髮。\n我不見兮、我心不說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼都人士、充耳琇實。\n彼君子女、謂之尹吉。\n我不見兮、我心苑結。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼都人士、垂帶而厲。\n彼君子女、卷髮如蠆。\n我不見兮、言從之邁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>匪伊垂之、帶則有餘。\n匪伊卷之、髮則有旟。\n我不見兮、云何盱矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">226 .  采綠\n終朝采綠、不盈一匊。\n予髮曲局、薄言歸沐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>終朝采藍、不盈一擔。\n五日為期、六日不儋。\n我不見兮、我心不說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼都人士、充耳琇實。\n彼君子女、謂之尹吉。\n我不見兮、我心苑結。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>彼都人士、垂帶而厲。\n彼君子女、卷髮如蠆。\n我不見兮、言從之邁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>匪伊垂之、帶則有餘。\n匪伊卷之、髮則有旟。\n我不見兮、云何盱矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">227.  黍苗\n芃芃黍苗、陰雨膏之。\n悠悠南行、召伯勞之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我任我輦、我車我牛。\n我行既集、蓋云歸哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我徒我御、我師我旅。\n我行既集、蓋云歸處。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肅肅謝功、召伯營之。\n烈烈征師、召伯成之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>原隰既平、泉流既清。\n召伯有成、王心則寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">228.  隰桑\n隰桑有阿、其葉有難。\n既見君子、其樂如何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>隰桑有阿、其葉有沃。\n既見君子、云何不樂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>隰桑有阿、其葉有幽。\n既見君子、德音孔膠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>心乎愛矣、遐不謂矣。\n中心藏之、何日忘之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">229.  白華\n白華菅兮、白茅束兮。\n之子之遠、俾我獨兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>英英白雲、露彼菅茅。\n天步艱難、之子不猶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>滮池北流、浸彼稻田。\n嘯歌傷懷、念彼碩人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>樵彼桑薪、卬烘于煁。\n維彼碩人、實勞我心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鼓鍾于宮、聲聞于外。\n念子懆懆、視我邁邁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有鶖在梁、有鶴在林。\n維彼碩人、實勞我心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鴛鴦在梁、戢其左翼。\n之子無良、二三其德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有扁斯石、履之卑兮。\n之子之遠、俾我疧兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">230.  綿蠻\n綿蠻黃鳥、止于丘阿。\n道之云遠、我勞如何。\n飲之食之、教之誨之、命彼後車、謂之載之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綿蠻黃鳥、止于丘隅。\n豈敢憚行、畏不能趨。\n飲之食之、教之誨之、命彼後車、謂之載之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>綿蠻黃鳥、止于丘側。\n豈敢憚行、畏不能極。\n飲之食之、教之誨之、命彼後車、謂之載之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">231.  瓠葉\n幡幡瓠葉、采之亨之。\n君子有酒、酌言嘗之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有兔斯首、炮之燔之。\n君子有酒、酌言獻之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有兔斯首、燔之炙之。\n君子有酒、酌言酢之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有兔斯首、燔之炮之。\n君子有酒、酌言酬之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">232.  漸漸之石\n漸漸之石、維其高矣。\n山川悠遠、維其勞矣。\n武人東征、不遑朝矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>漸漸之石、維其卒矣。\n山川悠遠、曷其沒矣。\n武人東征、不遑出矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有豕白蹢、烝涉波矣。\n月離于畢、俾滂沱矣。\n武人東征、不遑他矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">233.  苕之華\n苕之華、芸其黃矣。\n心之憂矣、維其傷矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>苕之華、其葉青青。\n知我如此、不如無生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>牂羊墳首、三星在罶。\n人可以食、鮮可以飽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">234.  何草不黃\n何草不黃、何日不行。\n何人不將、經營四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>何草不玄、何人不矜。\n哀我征夫、獨為匪民。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>匪兕匪虎、率彼曠野。\n哀我征夫、朝夕不暇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有芃者孤、率彼幽草。\n有棧之車、行彼周道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">大雅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>說見小雅\n文王之什\n235.  文王\n文王在上、於昭于天。\n周雖舊邦、其命維新。\n有周不顯、帝命不時。\n文王陟降、在帝左右。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>亹亹文王、令聞不已。\n陳錫哉周、侯文王孫子。\n文王孫子、本支百世。\n凡周之士、不顯亦世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>世之不顯、厥猶翼翼。\n思皇多士、生此王國。\n王國克生、維周之楨。\n濟濟多士、文王以寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>穆穆文王、於緝熙敬止。\n假哉天命、有商孫子。\n商之孫子、其麗不億。\n上帝既命、侯於周服。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>侯服于周、天命靡常。\n殷士膚敏、祼將于京。\n厥作祼將、常服黼冔。\n王之藎臣、無念爾祖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>無念爾祖、聿脩厥德。\n永言配命、自求多福。\n殷之未喪師、克配上帝。\n宜鑒于殷、駿命不易。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>命之不易、無遏爾躬。\n宣昭義問、有虞殷自天。\n上天之載、無聲無臭。\n儀刑文王、萬邦作孚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">236.  大明\n明明在下、赫赫在上。\n天難忱斯、不易維王。\n天位殷適、使不挾四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>摯仲氏任、自彼殷商、來嫁于周、曰嬪于京。\n乃及王季、維德之行。\n大任有身、生此文王。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維此文王、小心翼翼。\n昭事上帝、聿懷多福。\n厥德不回、以受方國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天監在下、有命既集。\n文王初載、天作之合。\n在洽之陽、在渭之涘。\n文王嘉止、大邦有子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>大邦有子、俔天之妹。\n文定厥祥、親迎于渭。\n造舟為梁、不顧其光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有命自天、命此文王。\n于周于京、纘女維莘。\n長子維行、篤生武王。\n保右命爾、燮伐大商。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>殷商之旅、其會如林。\n矢于牧野、維予侯興。\n上帝臨女、無貳爾心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>牧野洋洋、檀車煌煌、駟騵彭彭。\n維師尚父、時維鷹揚、涼彼武王、肆伐大商。\n會朝清明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">237.  綿\n綿綿瓜瓞。\n民之初生、自土沮漆。\n古公亶父、陶父陶穴、未有家室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>古公亶父、來朝走馬。\n率西水滸、至于岐下。\n爰及姜女、聿來胥宇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>周原膴膴、菫茶如飴。\n爰始爰謀、爰契我龜。\n曰止曰時、築室于茲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>迺慰迺止、迺左迺右、迺疆迺理、迺宣迺畝、自西徂東、周爰執事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乃召司空、乃召司徒、俾立室家。\n其繩則直、縮版以載、作廟翼翼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>捄之陾陾、度之薨薨、築之登登、削屢馮馮、百堵皆興、鼛鼓弗勝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>迺立皋門、皋門有伉。\n迺立應門、應門將將。\n迺立冢土、戎醜攸行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肆不殄厥慍、亦不隕厥問。\n柞棫拔矣、行道兌矣。\n混夷駾矣、維其喙矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>虞芮質厥成、文王蹶厥生。\n予曰有疏附、予曰有先後、予曰有奔奏、予曰有禦侮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">238.  棫樸\n芃芃棫樸。\n薪之槱之。\n濟濟辟王。\n左右趣之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>濟濟辟王。\n左右奉璋。\n奉璋峨峨。\n髦士攸宜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>淠彼涇舟。\n烝徒楫之。\n周王于邁。\n六師及之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>倬彼雲漢。\n為章于天。\n周王壽考。\n遐不作人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>追琢其章。\n金玉其相。\n勉勉我王。\n綱紀四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">239.  早麓\n瞻彼早麓、榛楛濟濟。\n豈弟君子、于祿豈弟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瑟彼玉瓚、黃流在中。\n其弟君子、福祿攸降。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳶飛戾天、魚躍于淵。\n豈弟君子、遐不作人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>清酒既載、騂牡既備。\n以享以祀、以介景福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瑟彼柞棫、民所燎矣。\n豈弟君子、神所勞矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>莫莫葛藟、施于條枚。\n豈弟君子、求福不回。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">240.  思齊\n思齊大任、文王之母、思媚周姜、京室之婦。\n大姒嗣徽音、則百斯男。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>惠于宗公、神罔時怨、神罔時恫。\n刑于寡妻、至于兄弟、以御于家邦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>雝雝在宮、肅肅在廟。\n不顯亦臨、無射亦保。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肆戎疾不殄、烈假不瑕。\n不聞亦式、不諫亦入。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肆成人有德、小子有造。\n古之人無斁、譽髦斯士。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">241.  皇矣\n皇矣上帝、臨下有赫。\n監觀四方、求民之莫。\n維此二國、其政不獲。\n維彼四國、爰究爰度。\n上帝耆之、憎其式廓。\n乃眷西顧、止維與宅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>作之屏之、其菑其翳。\n脩之平之、其灌其栵。\n啟之辟之、其檉其椐。\n攘之剔之、其其柘。\n帝遷明德、串夷載路。\n天立厥配、受命既固。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>帝省其山、柞棫斯拔、松柏斯兌。\n帝作邦作對、自大伯王季。\n維此王季、因心則友。\n則友其兄、則篤其慶。\n載錫之光、受祿無喪、奄有四方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維此王季、帝度其心、貊其德音。\n其德克明、克明克類、克長克君。\n王此大邦、克順克比。\n比于文王、其德靡悔。\n既受帝祉、施于孫子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>帝謂文王、無然畔援、無然歆羨、誕先登于岸。\n密人不恭、敢距大邦、侵阮徂共。\n王赫斯怒、爰整其旅、以按徂旅、以篤于周祜、以對于天下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>依其在京、侵自阮疆、陟我高岡。\n無矢我陵、我陵我阿。\n無飲我泉、我泉我池。\n度其鮮原、居歧之陽、在渭之將。\n萬邦之方、下民之王。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>帝謂文王、予懷明德、不大聲以色、不長夏以革。\n不識不知、順帝之則。\n帝謂文王、詢爾仇方、同爾兄弟、以爾鉤援、與爾臨衝、以我崇墉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>臨衝閑閑、崇墉言言。\n執訊連連、攸馘安安。\n是類是禡、是致是附。\n四方以無悔。\n臨衝茀茀、崇墉仡仡。\n是伐是肆、是絕是忽。\n四方以無拂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">242.  靈臺\n經始靈臺、經之營之。\n庶民攻之、不日成之。\n經始勿亟、庶民子來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王在靈囿、麀鹿攸伏、麀鹿濯濯、白鳥翯翯。\n王在靈沼、於牣魚躍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>虡業維樅、賁鼓維鏞。\n於論鼓鐘、於樂辟廱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>於論鼓鐘、於樂辟廱。\n鼉鼓逢逢、朦瞍奏公。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">243.  下武\n下武維周、世有哲王。\n三后在天、王配于京。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王配于京、世德作求。\n永言配命、成王之孚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>成王之孚、下土之式。\n永言考思、考思維則。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>媚茲一人、應侯順德。\n永言考思、昭哉嗣服。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昭茲來許、繩其祖武。\n於萬斯年、受天之祜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>受天之祜、四方來賀。\n於萬斯年、不遐有佐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">244.  文王有聲\n文王有聲、遹駿有聲。\n遹求厥寧、遹觀厥成。\n文王烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王受命、有此武功。\n既伐于崇、作邑于豐。\n文王烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>築城伊淢、作豐伊匹。\n匪棘其欲、遹追來孝。\n王后烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王公伊濯、為豐之垣。\n四方攸同、王后維翰。\n王后烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>豐水東注、維禹之績。\n四方攸同、皇王維辟。\n皇王烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鎬京辟廱。\n自西自東、自南自北、無思不服。\n皇王烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>考卜維王、宅是鎬京。\n維龜正之、武王成之。\n武王烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>豐水有芑、武王豈不仕。\n詒厥孫謀、以燕翼子。\n武王烝哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">生民之什\n245.  生民\n厥初生民、時維姜嫄。\n生民如何、克禋克祀、以弗無子。\n履帝武敏歆、攸介攸止、載震載夙、載生載育、時維后稷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誕彌厥月、先生如達、不坼不副、無菑無害。\n以赫厥靈、上帝不寧、不康禋祀、居然生子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誕寘之隘巷、牛羊腓字之。\n誕寘之平林、會伐平林。\n誕寘之寒冰、鳥覆翼之。\n鳥乃去矣、后稷呱矣、實覃實訏、厥聲載路。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誕實匍匐、克歧克嶷、以就口食。\n蓺之荏菽、荏菽旆旆、禾役穟穟、麻麥懞懞、瓜瓞唪唪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誕后稷之穡、有相之道。\n茀厥豐草、種之黃茂。\n實方實苞、實種實褎、實發實秀、實堅實好、實穎實栗。\n即有邰家室。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誕降嘉種、維秬維秠、維穈維芑。\n恆之秬秠、是穫是畝。\n恆之穈芑、是任是負。\n以歸肇祀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>誕我祀如何。\n或舂或揄、或簸或蹂。\n釋之叟叟、烝之浮浮。\n載謀載惟、取蕭祭脂、取羝以軷。\n載燔載烈、以興嗣歲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>卬盛于豆、于豆于登。\n其香始升、上帝居歆。\n胡臭亶時、后稷肇祀、庶無罪悔、以迄于今。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">246.  行葦\n敦彼行葦 。\n牛羊勿踐履 。\n方苞方體。\n維葉泥泥 。\n戚戚兄弟 。\n莫遠具爾。\n或肆之筵。\n或受之几。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肆筵設席。\n授几有緝御。\n或獻或酢。\n洗爵奠斝。\n醓醢以薦。\n或燔或灸。\n嘉殽脾臄。\n或歌或咢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>敦弓既鈞。\n舍矢既均。\n序賓以賢。\n敦弓既句。\n既挾四鍭。\n四鍭如樹。\n序賓以不侮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>曾孫維主。\n酒醴維醹。\n酌以大斗。\n以祈黃耇。\n黃耇台背。\n以引以翼。\n壽考維祺。\n以介景福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">247.  既醉\n既醉以酒、既飽以德。\n君子萬年、介爾景福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>既醉以酒、爾殽既將。\n君子萬年、介爾昭明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昭明有融、高朗令終。\n令終有俶、公尺嘉告。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其告維何、籩豆靜嘉。\n朋友攸攝、攝以威儀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>威儀孔時、君子有孝子。\n孝子不匱、永錫爾類。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其類維何、室家之壺。\n君子萬年、永錫祚胤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其胤維何、天被爾祿。\n君子萬年、景命有僕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其僕維何、釐爾女士。\n釐爾女士、從以孫子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">248.  鳧鷖\n鳧鷖在涇、公尺來燕來寧。\n爾酒既清、爾殽既馨、公尺燕飲、福祿來成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳧鷖在沙、公尺來燕來宜。\n爾酒既多、爾殽既嘉、公尺燕飲、福祿來為。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳧鷖在渚、公尺來燕來處。\n爾酒既湑、爾殽伊脯、公尺燕飲、福祿來下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳧鷖在潀、公尺來燕來宗。\n既燕于宗、福祿攸降。\n公尺燕飲、福祿來崇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳧鷖在亹、公尺來止熏熏。\n旨酒欣欣、燔炙芬芬、公尺燕飲、無有後艱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">249.  假樂\n假樂君子、顯顯令德。\n宜民宜人、受祿于天。\n保右命之、自天申之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>干祿百福、子孫千億。\n穆穆皇皇、宜君宜王。\n不愆不忘、率由舊章。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>威儀抑抑、德音秩秩。\n無怨無惡、率由群匹。\n受福無疆、四方之綱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>之綱之紀、燕及朋友。\n百辟卿士、媚于天子。\n不解于位、民之攸塈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">250.  公劉\n篤公劉、匪居匪康、迺埸迺疆、 迺機迺倉。\n迺裹餱糧、于橐于囊、 思輯用光 。\n弓矢斯張、干戈戚揚、爰方啟行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>篤公劉、于胥斯原、既庶既繁、既順迺宣、而無永歎。\n陟則在巘、復降在原。\n何以舟之、維玉及瑤、鞞琫容刀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>篤公劉、逝彼百泉、瞻彼溥原。\n迺陟南岡、乃覯于京。\n京師之野、于時處處、于時廬旅、于時言言、于時語語。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>篤公劉、于京斯依。\n蹌蹌濟濟、俾筵俾几。\n既登乃依。\n乃造其曹、執豕于牢、酌之用匏。\n食之飲之、君之宗之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>篤公劉、既溥既長、既景迺岡、相其陰陽、觀其流泉、其軍三單。\n度其隰原、徹田為糧。\n度其夕陽、豳居允荒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>篤公劉、于豳斯館。\n涉渭為亂、取厲取鍛。\n止基迺理、爰眾爰有。\n夾其皇澗、溯其過澗。\n止旅迺密、芮鞫之即。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">251.  泂酌\n泂酌彼行潦、挹彼注茲、可以饙饎。\n豈弟君子、民之父母 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>泂酌彼行潦、挹彼注茲、可以濯罍。\n豈弟君子、民之攸歸 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>洞酌彼行潦、挹彼注茲、可以濯溉。\n豈弟君子、民之攸塈 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">252.  卷阿\n有卷者阿、飄風自南。\n豈弟君子、來游來歌、以矢其音 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>伴奐爾游矣、優游爾休矣。\n豈弟君子、俾爾彌爾性、似先公酋矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爾土宇昄章、亦孔之厚矣。\n豈弟君子、俾爾彌爾性、百神爾主矣 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>爾受命長矣、茀祿爾康矣。\n豈弟君子、俾爾彌爾性、純嘏爾常矣 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有馮有翼、有孝有德、以引以翼。\n豈弟君子、四方為則 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>顒顒卬卬、如圭如璋、令聞令望。\n豈弟君子、四方為綱 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳳凰于飛、翽翽其羽、亦集爰止。\n藹藹王多吉士、維君子使、媚於天子 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳳凰于飛、翽翽其羽、亦傅于天。\n藹藹王多吉人、維君子命、媚于庶人 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鳳凰鳴矣、于彼高岡。\n梧桐生矣、于彼朝陽 。\n菶菶萋萋、雝雝喈喈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>君子之車、既庶且多。\n君子之馬、既閑且馳 。\n矢詩不多、維以遂歌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">253.  民勞\n民亦勞止、汔可小康。\n惠此中國、以綏四方 。\n無縱詭隨、以謹無良。\n式遏寇虐、憯不畏明 。\n柔遠能邇、以定我王。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>民亦勞止、汔可小休。\n惠此中國、以為民逑 。\n無縱詭隨、以謹惛怓。\n式遏寇虐、無俾民憂 。\n無棄爾勞、以為王休。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>民亦勞止、汔可小息。\n惠此京師、以綏四國 。\n無縱詭隨、以謹罔極。\n式遏寇虐、無俾作慝 。\n敬慎威儀、以近有德。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>民亦勞止、汔可小愒。\n惠此中國、俾民憂泄 。\n無縱詭隨、以謹醜厲。\n式遏寇虐、無俾正敗 。\n戎雖小子、而式弘大。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>民亦勞止、汔可小安。\n惠此中國、國無有殘 。\n無縱詭隨、以謹繾綣。\n式遏寇虐、無俾正反 。\n王欲玉女、是用大諫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">254.  板\n上帝板板、下民卒癉。\n出話不然、為猶不遠 。\n靡聖管管、不實於亶。\n猶之未遠、是用大諫 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天之方難、無然憲憲。\n天之方蹶、無然泄泄。\n辭之輯矣、民之冾矣。\n辭之懌矣、民之莫矣 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>我雖異事、及爾同僚。\n我即而謀、聽我囂囂。\n我言維服、勿以為笑。\n先民有言、詢于芻蕘 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天之方虐、無然謔謔。\n老夫灌灌、小子蹻蹻。\n匪我言耄、爾用憂謔。\n多將熇熇、不可救藥 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天之方懠、無為夸毗。\n威儀卒迷、善人載尸。\n民之方殿屎、則莫我敢葵。\n喪亂蔑資、曾莫惠我師 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天之牖民、如壎如篪。\n如璋如圭、如取如攜。\n攜無日益、牖民孔易。\n民之多辟、無自立辟 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>价人維藩、大師維垣、大邦維屏、大宗維翰、懷德維寧、宗子維城。\n無俾城壞、無獨斯畏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>敬天之怒、無敢戲豫。\n敬天之渝、無敢馳驅。\n昊天曰明、及爾出王。\n昊天曰旦、及爾游衍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">蕩之什\n255.  蕩\n蕩蕩上帝、下民之辟。\n疾威上帝、其命多辟。\n天生烝民、其命匪諶。\n靡不有初、鮮克有終。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王曰咨、咨女殷商。\n曾是彊禦、曾是掊克。\n曾是在位、曾是在服。\n天降慆德、女興是力 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王曰咨、咨女殷商。\n而秉義類 、彊禦多懟。\n流言以對、寇攘式內。\n侯作侯祝、靡屆靡究 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王曰咨、咨女殷商。\n女炰烋于中國、歛怨以為德。\n不明爾德、時無背無側 。\n爾德不明、以無陪無卿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王曰咨、咨女殷商。\n天不湎爾以酒、不義從式。\n既愆爾止、靡明靡晦。\n式號式呼、俾晝作夜 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王曰咨、咨女殷商。\n如蜩如螗、如沸如羹。\n小大近喪、人尚乎由行。\n內奰于中國、覃及鬼方 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王曰咨、咨女殷商。\n匪上帝不時、殷不用舊。\n雖無老成人、尚有典刑。\n曾是莫聽、大命以傾 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>文王曰咨、咨女殷商。\n人亦有言、顛沛之揭。\n枝葉未有害、本實先撥。\n殷鑒不遠、在夏后之世 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">256.  抑\n抑抑威儀、維德之隅。\n人亦有言、靡哲不愚。\n庶人之愚、亦職維疾。\n哲人之愚、亦維斯戾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>無競維人、四方其訓之。\n有覺德行、四國順之。\n訏謨定命、遠猶辰告。\n敬慎威儀、維民之則。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>其在于今、興迷亂于政。\n顛覆厥德、荒湛于酒。\n女雖湛樂從、弗念厥紹。\n罔敷求先生、克共明刑 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肆皇天弗尚、如彼泉流、無淪胥以亡。\n夙興夜寐、洒掃廷內、維民之章。\n脩爾車馬、弓矢戎兵。\n用戒戎作、用逖蠻方 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>質爾人民、謹爾侯度、用戒不虞。\n慎爾出話、敬爾威儀、無不柔嘉。\n白圭之玷、尚可磨也。\n斯言之玷、不可為也 。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>無易由言、無日苟矣。\n莫捫朕舌、言不可逝矣。\n無言不讎、無德不報。\n惠于朋友、庶民小子、子孫繩繩、萬民靡不承。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>視爾友君子、輯柔爾顏、不遐有愆。\n相在爾室、尚不媿于屋漏。\n無曰不顧、莫予云覯。\n神之格思、不可度思、矧可射思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>辟爾為德、俾藏俾嘉。\n淑慎爾止、不愆于儀。\n不僭不賊、鮮不為則。\n投我以桃、報之以李。\n彼童而角、實虹小子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>荏染柔木、言緡之絲。\n溫溫恭人、維德之基。\n其維哲人、告之話言、順德之行。\n其維愚人、覆謂我僭。\n民各有心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>於乎小子、未知藏否。\n匪手攜之、言示之事。\n匪面命之、言提其耳。\n借日未知、亦既抱子。\n民之靡盈、誰夙知而莫成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昊天孔昭、我生靡樂。\n視爾夢夢、我心慘慘。\n誨爾諄諄、聽我藐藐。\n匪用為教、覆用為虐。\n借日未知、亦聿既耄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>於乎小子、告爾舊子。\n聽用我謀、庶無大悔。\n天方艱難、日喪厥國。\n取譬不遠、昊天不忒。\n回遹其德、俾民大棘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">257.  桑柔\n菀彼桑柔、其下侯旬。\n捋采其劉、瘼此下民。\n不殄心憂、倉兄填兮。\n倬彼昊天、寧不我矜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四牡騤騤、旟旐有翩。\n亂生不夷、靡國不泯。\n民靡有黎、具禍以燼。\n於乎有哀、國步斯頻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>國步蔑資、天不我將。\n靡所止疑、云徂何往。\n君子實維、秉心無競。\n誰生厲階、至今為梗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>憂心慇慇、念我土宇。\n我生不辰、逢天僤努。\n自西徂東、靡所定處。\n多我覯痻、孔棘我圉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>為謀為毖、亂況斯削。\n告爾憂恤、誨爾序爵。\n誰能執熱、逝不以濯。\n其何能淑、載胥及溺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>如彼溯風、亦孔之僾。\n民有肅心、荓云不逮。\n好是稼穡、力民代食。\n稼穡維寶、代食維好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天降喪亂、滅我立王。\n降此蟊賊、稼穡卒痒。\n哀恫中國、具贅卒荒。\n靡有旅力、以念穹蒼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維此惠君、民人所瞻。\n秉心宣猶、考慎其相。\n維彼不順、自獨俾臧。\n自有肺腸、俾民卒狂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻彼中林、甡甡其鹿。\n朋友已譖、不胥以穀。\n人亦有言、進退維谷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維此聖人、瞻言百里。\n維彼愚人、覆狂以喜。\n匪言不能、胡斯畏忌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維此良人、弗求弗迪。\n維彼忍心、是顧是復。\n民之貪亂、寧為荼毒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>大風有隧、有空大谷。\n維此良人、作為式穀。\n維彼不順、征以中垢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>大風有隧、貪人敗類。\n聽言則對、誦言如醉。\n匪用其良、覆俾我悖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>嗟爾朋友、予豈不知而作。\n如彼飛蟲、時亦弋獲。\n既之陰女、反予來赫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>民之罔極、職涼善背。\n為民不利、如云不克。\n民之回遹、職競用力。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>民之未戾、職盜為寇。\n涼曰不可、覆背善詈。\n雖曰匪予、既作爾歌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">258.  雲漢\n倬彼雲漢、昭回于天。\n王曰於乎、何辜今之人。\n天降喪亂、饑饉薦臻。\n靡神不舉、靡愛斯牲。\n圭璧既卒、寧莫我聽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>旱既大甚、蘊隆蟲蟲。\n不殄禋祀、自郊徂宮。\n上下尊瘞、靡神不宗。\n后稷不克、上帝不臨。\n耗斁下土、寧丁我躬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>旱既大甚、則不可推。\n兢兢業業、如霆如雷。\n周餘黎民、靡有孑遺。\n昊天上帝、則我不遺。\n胡不相畏、先祖于摧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>旱既大甚、則不可沮。\n赫赫炎炎、云我無所。\n大命近止、靡瞻靡顧。\n群公先正、則不我助。\n父母先祖、胡寧忍予。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>旱既大甚、滌滌山川。\n旱魃為虐、如惔如焚。\n我心憚暑、憂心如熏。\n群公先正、則不我聞。\n昊天上帝、寧俾我遯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>旱既大甚、黽勉畏去。\n胡寧瘨我以旱、憯不知其故。\n祈年孔夙、方社不莫。\n昊天上帝、則我不虞。\n敬恭明神、宜無悔怒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>旱既大甚、散無友紀。\n鞫哉庶正、疚哉冢宰。\n趣馬師氏、膳夫左右。\n靡人不周、無不能正。\n瞻卬昊天、云如何里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>瞻卬昊天、有嘒其星。\n大夫君子、昭假無嬴。\n大命近止、無棄爾成。\n何求為我、以戾庶正。\n瞻卬昊天、曷惠其寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">259.  崧高\n崧高維嶽、駿極于天。\n維嶽降神、生甫及申。\n維申及甫、維周之翰。\n四國于蕃、四方于宣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>亹亹申伯、王纘之事。\n于邑于謝、南國是式。\n王命召伯、定申伯之宅。\n登是南邦、世執其功。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王命申伯、式是南邦。\n因是謝人、以作爾庸。\n王命召伯、徹申伯土田。\n王命傅御、遷其私人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>申伯之功、召伯是營。\n有俶其城、寢廟既成。\n既成藐藐、王錫申伯。\n四牡蹻蹻、鉤膺濯濯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王遣申伯、路車乘馬。\n我圖爾居、莫如南土。\n錫爾介圭、以作爾寶。\n往近王舅、南土是保。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>申伯信邁、王餞于郿。\n申伯還南、謝于誠歸。\n王命召伯、徹申伯土疆。\n以峙其粻、式遄其行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>申伯番番、既入于謝、徒御嘽嘽。\n周邦咸喜、戎有良翰。\n不顯申伯、王之元舅、文武是憲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>申伯之德、柔惠且直。\n揉此萬邦、聞于四國。\n吉甫作誦、其詩孔碩、其風肆好、以贈申伯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">260.  烝民\n天生烝民、有物有則。\n民之秉彝、好是懿德。\n天監有周、昭假于下、保茲天子、生仲山甫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>仲山甫之德、柔嘉維則。\n令儀令色、小心翼翼。\n古訓是式、威儀是力、天子是若、明命使賦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王命仲山甫、式是百辟。\n纘戎祖考、王躬是保。\n出納王命、王之喉舌。\n賦政于外、四方爰發。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>肅肅王命、仲山甫將之。\n邦國若否、仲山甫明之。\n既明且哲、以保其身。\n夙夜匪解、以事一人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>人亦有言、柔則茹之、剛則吐之。\n維仲山甫、柔亦不茹、剛亦不吐、不侮矜寡、不畏疆禦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>人亦有言、德輶如毛、民鮮克舉之。\n我儀圖之、維仲山甫舉之、愛莫助之。\n袞職有闕、維仲山甫補之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>仲山甫出祖、四牡業業、征夫捷捷、每懷靡及。\n四牡彭彭、八鸞鏘鏘。\n王命仲山甫、城彼東方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四牡騤騤、八鸞喈喈。\n仲山甫徂齊、式遄其歸。\n吉甫作誦、穆如清風。仲山甫永懷、以慰其心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">261.  韓奕\n奕奕梁山、維禹甸之、有倬其道。\n韓侯受命、王親命之、纘戎祖考。\n無廢朕命、夙夜匪解。\n虔共爾位、朕命不易。\n榦不庭方、以佐戎辟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>四牡奕奕、孔脩且張。\n韓侯入覲、以其介圭、入覲于王。\n王錫韓侯、淑旂綏章。\n簟茀錯衡。\n玄袞赤舄、鉤膺鏤錫、鞹鞃淺幭、鞗革金厄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>韓侯出祖、出宿于屠。\n顯父餞之、清酒百壺。\n其殽維何、炰鱉鮮魚。\n其蔌維何、維筍及蒲。\n其贈維何、乘馬路車。\n籩豆有且、侯氏燕胥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>韓侯取妻、汾王之甥、蹶父之子。\n韓侯迎止、于蹶之里。\n百兩彭彭、八鸞鏘鏘、不顯其光。\n諸娣從之、祁祁如雲。\n韓侯顧之、爛其盈門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>蹶父孔武、靡國不到。\n為韓姞相攸、莫如韓樂。\n孔樂韓土、川澤訏訏、魴鱮甫甫、麀鹿噳噳、有熊有羆、有貓有虎。\n慶既令居、韓姞燕譽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>溥彼韓城、燕師所完。\n以先祖受命、因時百蠻。\n王錫韓侯、其追其貊、奄受北國、因以其伯。\n實墉實壑、實畝實籍、獻其貔皮、赤豹黃羆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">262.  江漢\n江漢浮浮、武夫滔滔。\n匪安匪遊、淮夷來求。\n既出我車、既設我旟。\n匪安匪舒、淮夷來鋪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>江漢湯湯、武夫洸洸。\n經營四方、告成于王。\n四方既平、王國庶定。\n時靡有爭、王心載寧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>江漢之滸、王命昭虎、式辟四方、徹我疆土。\n匪疚匪棘、王國來極。\n于理于理、至于南海。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王命昭虎、來旬來宣。\n文武受命、召公維翰。\n無曰予小子、召公是似。\n肇敏戎公、用錫爾祉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>釐爾圭瓚、鬯一卣。\n告于文人、錫山土田。\n于周受命、自召祖命。\n虎拜稽首、天子萬年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>虎拜稽首、對揚王休、作召公考、天子萬壽。\n明明天子、令聞不已、矢其文德、洽此四國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">263.  常武\n赫赫明明、王命卿士、南仲大祖、大師皇父。\n整我六師、以脩我戎。\n既敬既戒、惠此南國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王謂尹氏、命程伯休父。\n左右陳行、戒我師旅。\n率彼淮浦、省此徐土。\n不留不處、三事就緒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>赫赫業業、有嚴天子。\n王舒保作、匪紹匪遊、徐方繹騷。\n震驚徐方、如雷如霆、徐方震驚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王奮厥武、如震如怒。\n進厥虎臣、闞如虓虎。\n鋪敦淮濆、仍執醜虜。\n截彼淮浦、王師之所。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王旅嘽嘽、如飛如翰、如江如漢、如山之苞、\n如川之流、綿綿翼翼、不測不克、濯征徐國。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>王猶允塞、徐方既來。\n徐方既同、天子之功。\n四方既平、徐方來庭。\n徐方不回、王曰還歸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">264.  瞻卬\n瞻卬昊天、則我不惠。\n孔填不寧、降此大厲。\n邦靡有定、士民其瘵。\n蟊賊蟊疾、靡有夷屆。\n罪罟不收、靡有夷瘳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>人有土田、女反有之。\n人有民人、女覆奪之。\n此宜無罪、女反收之。\n彼宜有罪、女覆說之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>哲夫成城、哲婦傾城。\n懿厥哲婦、為梟為鴟。\n婦有長舌、維厲之階。\n亂匪降自天、生自婦人。\n匪教匪誨、時維婦寺。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>鞫人忮忒、譖始竟背。\n豈曰不極、伊胡為慝。\n如賈三倍、君子是識。\n婦無公事、休其蠶織。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天何以刺、何神不富。\n舍爾介狄、維予胥忌。\n不弔不祥、威儀不類。\n人之云亡、邦國殄瘁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天之降罔、維其優儀。\n人之云亡、心之憂矣。\n天之降罔、維其幾矣。\n人之云亡、心之悲矣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>觱沸檻泉、維其深矣。\n心之憂矣、寧自今矣。\n不自我先、不自我後。\n藐藐昊天、無不克鞏。\n無忝皇祖、式救爾後。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">265.  召旻\n旻天疾威、天篤降喪。\n瘨我饑饉、民卒流亡。\n我居圉卒荒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天降罪罟、蟊賊內訌、昏椓靡共、\n潰潰回遹、實靖夷我邦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>皋皋訿訿、曾不知其玷。\n兢兢業業、孔填不寧、我位孔貶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>如彼歲早、草不潰茂。\n如彼棲苴。\n我相此邦、無不潰止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維昔之富、不如時、維今之疚、不如茲。\n彼疏斯粺、胡不自替、職兄斯引。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>池之竭矣、不云自頻。\n泉之竭矣、不云自中。\n溥斯害矣、職兄斯弘、不災我躬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昔先王受命、有如召公、日辟國百里。\n今也日蹙國百里。\n於乎哀哉、維今之人、不尚有舊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">頌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>周頌清廟之什\n266.  清廟\n於穆清廟、肅雝顯相。\n濟濟多士、秉文之德。\n對越在天、駿奔走在廟。\n不顯不承、無射於人斯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">267.  維天之命\n維天之命、於穆不已。\n於乎不顯、文王之德之純。\n假以溢我、我其收之。\n駿惠我文王、曾孫篤之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">268.  維清\n維清緝熙、文王之典。\n肇禋、迄用有成、維周之禎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">269.  烈文\n烈文辟公、錫茲祉福。\n惠我無疆、子孫保之。\n無封靡于爾邦、維王其崇之。\n念茲戎功、繼序其皇之。\n無競維人、四方其訓之。\n不顯維德、百辟其刑之。\n於乎前王不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">270.  天作\n天作高山、大王荒之。\n彼作矣、文王康之。\n彼徂矣岐、有夷之行、子孫保之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">271.  昊天有成命\n昊天有成命、二后受之。\n成王不敢康、夙夜基命宥密。\n於緝熙、單厥心。\n肆其靖之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">272.  我將\n我將我享、維羊維牛、維天其右之。\n儀式刑文王之典、日靖四方。\n伊嘏文王、既右享之。\n我其夙夜、畏天之威、于時保之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">273.  時邁\n時邁其邦、昊天其子之。\n實右序有周。\n薄言震之、莫不震疊。\n懷柔百神、及河喬嶽。\n允王維后。\n明昭有周、式序在位。\n載戢干戈、載櫜弓矢。\n我求懿德、肆于時夏。\n允王保之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">274.  執競\n執競武王、無競維烈。\n不顯成康、上帝是皇。\n自彼成康、奄有四方、斤斤其明。\n鐘鼓喤喤、磬筦將將、降福穰穰。\n降福簡簡、威儀反反。\n既醉既飽、福祿來反。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">275.  思文\n思文后稷、克配彼天、立我烝民、莫匪爾極。\n貽我來牟、帝命率育。\n無比疆爾界、陳常于時夏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">周頌臣工之什\n276.  臣工\n嗟嗟臣工、敬爾在公。\n王釐爾成、來咨來茹。\n嗟嗟保介、維莫之春、亦又何求、如何新畬。\n於皇來牟、將受厥明。\n明昭上帝、迄用康年。\n命我眾人、庤乃錢鎛、奄觀銍艾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">277.  噫嘻\n噫嘻成王、既昭假爾。\n率時農夫、播厥百穀。\n駿發爾私、終三十里。\n亦服爾耕、十千維耦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">278.  振鷺\n振鷺于飛、于彼西雝。\n我客戾止、亦有斯容。\n在彼無惡、在此無斁。\n庶幾夙夜、以永終譽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">279.  豐年\n豐年多黍多稌。\n亦有高廩、萬億及秭。\n為酒為醴、烝畀祖妣、以洽百禮。\n降福孔皆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">280.  有瞽\n有瞽有瞽、在周之庭。\n崇牙樹羽、應田縣鼓、 磬柷圉。\n既備乃奏。\n簫管備舉。\n喤喤厥聲、肅雝和鳴、先祖先聽。\n我客戾止、永觀厥成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">281.  潛\n猗與漆沮、潛有多魚、有鱣有鮪、鰷鱨鰋鯉。\n以享以祀、以介景福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">282.  雝\n有來雝雝、至止肅肅。\n相維辟公、天子穆穆。\n於薦廣牡、相予肆祀。\n假哉皇考、綏予孝子。\n宣哲維人、文武維后。\n燕及皇天、克昌厥後。\n綏我眉壽、介以繁祉。\n既友烈考、亦友文母。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">283.  載見\n載見辟王、曰求厥章。\n龍旂陽陽、和鈴央央。\n鞗革有鶬、休有烈光。\n率見昭考、以考以享、以介眉壽。\n永言保之、思皇多祜。\n烈文辟公、綏以多福、俾緝熙于純嘏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">284.  有客\n有客有客、亦白其馬。\n有萋有且、敦琢其旅。\n有客宿宿、有客信信。\n言授之縶、以縶其馬。\n薄言追之、左右綏之。\n既有淫威、降福孔夷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">285.  武\n於皇武王、無競維烈。\n允文文王、克開厥後。\n嗣武受之、勝殷遏劉、耆定爾功。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">周頌閔予小子之什\n286.  閔予小子\n閔予小子、遭家不造、嬛嬛在疚。\n於乎皇考、永世克考。\n念茲皇祖、陟降庭止。\n維予小子、夙夜敬止。\n於乎皇王、繼序思不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">287.  訪落\n訪予落止、率時昭考。\n於乎悠哉、朕未有艾。\n將予就之、繼猶判渙。\n維予小子、未堪家多難。\n紹庭上下、陟降厥家。\n休矣皇考、以保明其身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">288.  敬之\n敬之敬之、天維顯思、命不易哉。\n無曰高高在上、陟降厥士、日監在茲。\n維予小子、不聰敬止。\n日就月將、學有緝熙于光明。\n佛時仔肩、示我顯德行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">289.  小毖\n予其懲 。\n而毖後患。\n莫予荓蜂。\n自求辛螫。\n肇允彼桃蟲。\n拚飛維鳥。\n未堪家多難。\n予又集于蓼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">290.  載芟\n載芟載柞、其耕澤澤。\n千耦其耘、徂濕徂畛。\n侯主侯伯、侯亞侯旅、侯疆侯以。\n有嗿其饁、思媚其婦、有依其士。\n有略其耜、俶載南畝。\n播厥百殼、實函斯活。\n驛驛其達、有厭其傑。\n厭厭其苗、綿綿其麃。\n載穫濟濟、有實其積、萬億及秭。\n為酒為醴、烝畀祖妣、以洽百體。\n有飶其香、邦家之光。\n有椒其馨、胡考之寧。\n匪且有且、匪今斯今、振古如茲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">291.  良耜\n畟畟良耜、俶載南畝。\n播厥百殼、實函斯活。\n或來瞻女、載筐及筥、其饟伊黍。\n其笠伊糾、其鎛斯趙、以薅荼蓼。\n荼蓼朽止、黍稷茂止。\n穫之挃挃、積之栗栗。\n其崇如墉、其比如櫛。\n以開百室。\n百室盈止、婦子寧止。\n殺時犉牡、有捄其角。\n以似以續、續古之人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">292.  絲衣\n絲衣其紑、載弁俅俅。\n自堂徂基、自羊徂牛。\n鼐鼎及鼒、兕觥其觩。\n旨酒思柔。\n不吳不敖、胡考之休。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">293.  酌\n於鑠王師、遵養時晦。\n時純熙矣、是用大介。\n我龍受之、蹻蹻王之造。\n載用有嗣、實維爾公允師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">294.  桓\n綏萬邦、婁豐年。\n天命匪解。\n桓桓武王、保有厥士。\n于以四方、克定厥家。\n於昭于天。\n皇以閒之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">295.  賚\n文王既勤止、我應受之。\n敷時繹思、我徂維求定。\n時周之命、於繹思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">296.  般\n於皇時周。\n陟其高山、嶞山喬嶽、允猶翕河。\n敷天之下、裒時之對、時周之命。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">魯頌\n297.  駉\n駉駉牡馬、在坰之野。\n薄言駉者、有驈有皇、有驪有黃、以車彭彭。\n思無疆、思馬斯臧。\n駉駉牡馬、在坰之野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>薄言駉者、有騅有駓、有騂有騏、以車伾伾。\n思無期、思馬斯才。\n駉駉牡馬、在坰之野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>薄言駉者、有驒有駱、有騮有雒、以車繹繹。\n思無斁、思馬斯才。\n駉駉牡馬、在坰之野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>薄言駉者、有駰有騢、有驔有魚、以車祛祛。\n思無邪、思馬斯徂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">298.  有駜\n有駜有駜、駜彼乘黃。\n夙夜在公、在公明明。\n振振鷺、鷺于下。\n鼓咽咽、醉言舞。\n于胥樂兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有駜有駜、駜彼乘牡。\n夙夜在公、在公飲酒。\n振振鷺、鷺于飛。\n鼓咽咽、醉言歸。\n于胥樂兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>有駜有駜、駜彼乘駽。\n夙夜在公、在公載燕。\n自今以始、歲其有。\n君子有殼、詒孫子。\n于胥樂兮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">299.  泮水\n思樂泮水、薄采其芹。\n魯侯戾止、言觀其旂。\n其旂茷茷、鸞聲噦噦。\n無小無大、從公于邁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>思樂泮水、薄采其藻。\n魯侯戾止、其馬蹻蹻。\n其馬蹻蹻、其音昭昭。\n載色載笑、匪怒伊教。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>思樂泮水、薄采其茆。\n魯侯戾止、在泮飲酒。\n既飲旨酒、永錫難老。\n順彼長道、屈此群醜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>穆穆魯侯、敬明其德。\n敬慎威儀、維民之則。\n允文允武、昭假烈祖。\n靡有不孝、自求伊祜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>明明魯侯、克明其德。\n既作泮宮、淮夷攸服。\n矯矯虎臣、在泮獻馘。\n淑問如皋陶、在泮獻囚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>濟濟多士、克廣德心。\n桓桓于征、狄彼東南。\n烝烝皇皇、不吳不揚。\n不告于、在泮獻功。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>角弓其觩、束矢其搜。\n戎車孔博、徒御無斁。\n既克淮夷、孔淑不逆。\n式固爾猶、淮夷卒獲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>翩彼飛鴞、集于泮林、食我桑黮、懷我好音。\n憬彼淮夷、來獻其琛、元龜象齒、大賂南金。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">300.  閟宮\n閟宮有侐、實實枚枚。\n赫赫姜嫄、其德不回。\n上帝是依、無災無害。\n彌月不遲、是生后稷、降之百福。\n黍稷重穋、植稚菽麥。\n奄有下國、俾民稼穡、有稷有黍、有稻有秬。\n奄有下土、纘禹之緒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>后稷之孫、實維大王。\n居岐之陽、實始翦商。\n至于文武、纘大王之緒。\n致天之屆、于牧之野。\n無貳無虞、上帝臨女。\n敦商之旅、克咸厥功。\n王曰叔父、建爾元子、俾侯于魯。\n大啟爾宇、為周室輔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>乃命魯公、俾侯于東。\n錫之山川、土田附庸。\n周公職孫、莊公之子。\n龍旂承祀、六轡耳耳。\n春秋匪解、享祀不忒。\n皇皇后帝、皇祖后稷。\n享以騂犧、是饗是宜。\n降福既多、周公皇祖、亦其福女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>秋而載嘗、夏而楅衡。\n白牡騂剛、犧尊將將。\n毛炰胾羹、籩豆大房。\n萬舞洋洋、孝孫有慶。\n俾爾熾而昌、俾爾壽而藏。\n保彼東方、魯邦是常。\n不虧不崩、不震不騰。\n三壽作朋、如岡如陵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>公車千乘、朱英綠縢、二矛重弓。\n公徒三萬、貝冑朱綅。\n烝徒增增、戎狄是膺。\n荊舒適懲、則莫我敢承。\n俾爾昌而熾、俾爾壽而富、黃髮台背、壽胥與試。\n俾爾昌而大、俾爾耆而艾、萬有千歲、眉壽無有害。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>泰山巖巖、魯邦所詹。\n奄有龜蒙、遂荒大東、貝冑朱綅。\n至于海邦、淮夷來同。\n莫不率從、魯侯之功。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>保有鳧繹、遂荒徐宅。\n至于海邦、淮夷蠻貊。\n及彼南夷、莫不率從。\n莫敢不諾、魯侯是若。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天錫公純嘏、眉壽保魯。\n居常與許、復周公之宇。\n魯侯燕喜、令妻壽母。\n宜大夫庶士、邦國是有。\n既多受祉、黃髮兒齒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>徂來之松、新甫之柏。\n是斷是度、是尋是尺。\n松桷有舄、路寢孔碩。\n新廟奕奕、奚斯所作。\n孔曼且碩、萬民是若。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">商頌\n301.  那\n猗與那與、置我鼓。\n奏鼓簡簡、衎我烈祖。\n湯孫奏假、綏我思成。\n鼓淵淵、嘒嘒管聲。\n既和且平、依我聲聲。\n於赫湯孫、穆穆厥聲。\n庸鼓有斁、萬舞有奕。\n我有嘉客、亦不夷懌。\n自古在昔、先民有作。\n溫恭朝夕、執事有恪。\n顧予烝嘗、湯孫之將。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">302.  烈祖\n嗟嗟烈祖、有秩斯祜。\n申錫無疆、及爾思所。\n既載清酤、賚我思成。\n亦有和羹、既戒既平。\n鬷假無言、時靡有爭。\n綏我眉壽、黃耇無疆。\n約軧錯衡、八鸞鶬鶬。\n以假以享、我受命溥將。\n自天降康、豐年穰穰。\n來假來饗、降福無疆。\n顧予烝嘗、湯孫之將。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">303.  玄鳥\n天命玄鳥、降而生商、宅殷土芒芒。\n古帝命武湯、正域彼四方。\n方命厥后、奄有九有。\n商之先后、受命不殆、在武丁孫子。\n武丁孫子、武王靡不勝。\n龍旂十乘、大饎是承。\n邦畿千里、維民所止、肇域彼四海。\n四海來假、來假祁祁、景員維河。\n殷受命咸宜、百祿是何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">304.  長發\n濬哲維商、長發其祥。\n洪水芒芒、禹敷下土方、外大國是疆。\n幅隕既長、有娀方將、帝立子生商。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>玄王桓撥、受小國是達、受大國是達。\n率履不越、遂視既發。\n相土烈烈、海外有截。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>帝命不違、至于湯齊。\n湯降不遲、聖敬日躋。\n昭假遲遲、上帝是祗、帝命式于九圍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>受小球大球、為下國綴旒。\n何天之休、不競不絿、不剛不柔、敷政優優、百祿是遒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>受小共大共、為下國駿厖。\n何天之龍、敷奏其勇、不震不動、不戁不竦、百祿是總。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>武王載旆、有虔秉鉞。\n如火烈烈、則莫我敢曷。\n苞有三蘗、莫遂莫達、九有有截。\n韋顧既伐、昆吾夏桀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>昔在中葉、有震且業。\n允也天子、降于鄉士、實維阿衡、實左右商王。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">305.  殷武\n撻彼殷武、奮伐荊楚。\n深入其阻、裒荊之旅。\n有截有所、湯孫之緒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>維女荊楚、居國南鄉。\n昔有成湯、自彼氐羌、莫幹不來享、莫幹不來王、曰商是常。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天命多辟、設都于禹之績。\n歲事來辟、勿予禍適、稼穡匪解。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>天命降監、下民有嚴。\n不僭不濫、不敢怠遑。\n命于下國、封建厥福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>商邑翼翼、四方之極。\n赫赫厥聲、濯濯厥靈。\n壽考且寧、以保我後生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>陟彼景山、松柏丸丸。\n是斷是遷、方斲是虔。\n松桷有梴、旅楹有閑、寢成孔安。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">End of the Project Gutenberg EBook of Shi-Jing, by Anonymous</p></div>"
        },
