        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>Project Gutenberg-tm depends upon and cannot survive without wide\nspread public support and donations to carry out its mission of\nincreasing the number of public domain and licensed works that can be\nfreely distributed in machine readable form accessible by the widest\narray of equipment including outdated equipment.  Many small donations\n($1 to $5,000) are particularly important to maintaining tax exempt\nstatus with the IRS.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>The Foundation is committed to complying with the laws regulating\ncharities and charitable donations in all 50 states of the United\nStates.  Compliance requirements are not uniform and it takes a\nconsiderable effort, much paperwork and many fees to meet and keep up\nwith these requirements.  We do not solicit donations in locations\nwhere we have not received written confirmation of compliance.  To\nSEND DONATIONS or determine the status of compliance for any\nparticular state visit http://pglaf.org</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>While we cannot and do not solicit contributions from states where we\nhave not met the solicitation requirements, we know of no prohibition\nagainst accepting unsolicited donations from donors in such states who\napproach us with offers to donate.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>International donations are gratefully accepted, but we cannot make\nany statements concerning tax treatment of donations received from\noutside the United States.  U.S. laws alone swamp our small staff.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>Please check the Project Gutenberg Web pages for current donation\nmethods and addresses.  Donations are accepted in a number of other\nways including checks, online payments and credit card donations.\nTo donate, please visit: http://pglaf.org/donate</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 5.  General Information About Project Gutenberg-tm electronic\nworks.</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>Professor Michael S. Hart is the originator of the Project Gutenberg-tm\nconcept of a library of electronic works that could be freely shared\nwith anyone.  For thirty years, he produced and distributed Project\nGutenberg-tm eBooks with only a loose network of volunteer support.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Project Gutenberg-tm eBooks are often created from several printed\neditions, all of which are confirmed as Public Domain in the U.S.\nunless a copyright notice is included.  Thus, we do not necessarily\nkeep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Most people start at our Web site which has the main PG search facility:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>     http://www.gutenberg.org<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/00f0bdac837f6616/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-f09fcd twpub-00f0bdac837f6616-6b4cd0\"><p>This Web site includes information about Project Gutenberg-tm,\nincluding how to make donations to the Project Gutenberg Literary\nArchive Foundation, how to help produce our new eBooks, and how to\nsubscribe to our email newsletter to hear about new eBooks.</p></div>"
        },
